orts%20CEO%20Paul%20Griffiths%20said%20designs%20were%20being%20drawn%20up%20for%20Al%20Maktoum%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20will%20be%20built%20on%20the%20city's%20outskirts%20and%20should%20replace%20Dubai%20International%20in%20the%202030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20Dubai%20Airshow%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20where%20airlines%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20new%20planes.%20Last%20year%2C%20neighbouring%20Saudi%20Arabia%20announced%20plans%20for%20a%20major%20new%20air%20hub%20in%20Riyadh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we've%20reached%20about%20120%20million%20(passengers%20a%20year)%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20think%20our%20total%20capacity%20at%20DXB%20(Dubai%20International)%20is%20at%20the%20absolute%20maximum%20with%20everything%20optimised%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20need%20a%20new%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffiths%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20going%20to%20have%20to%20happen%20at%20some%20stage%20during%20the%202030s.%20We're%20going%20to%20be%20working%20on%20those%20designs%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20trajectory%20is%20good.%20The%20confidence%20in%20the%20industry%20remains%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGriffiths%20was%20speaking%20as%20new%20figures%20forecast%2086.9%20million%20passengers%20at%20Dubai%20International%20this%20year%2C%20surpassing%202019%20traffic%20and%20underlining%20the%20recovery%20from%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird-quarter%20traffic%20was%2022.9%20million%2C%20the%20highest%20since%202019%2C%20taking%202023%20numbers%20so%20far%20to%2064.5%20million%2C%20nearly%2040%20percent%20higher%20than%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Little%20impact'%20from%20Gaza%20war%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassenger%20numbers%20have%20not%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20hit%20regional%20economies%20and%20especially%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20little%20impact%20of%20traffic%20to%20the%20north%26quot%3B%2C%20Griffiths%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20in%20some%20regions%20it's%20got%20even%20stronger%20than%20before%2C%20so%20(there%20was)%20no%20impact%20that%20was%20discernible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20always%20knew%20when%20the%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20there'd%20be%20an%20equal%20and%20strong%20recovery%20because%20people%20under%20lockdown%20for%20two%20years%20were%20denied%20the%20ability%20to%20travel.%20And%20so%20that's%20why%20we've%20bounced%20back%20so%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubai%20airport%20closed%20briefly%20to%20commercial%20flights%20from%20March%20to%20July%202020%20for%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20travel%20hubs%20to%20reopen.%20In%202020%2C%20it%20received%20only%2025.9%20million%20passengers%2C%20down%20from%2086%20million%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20price%20tag%20or%20capacity%20has%20been%20set%20for%20the%20new%20airport%2C%20Griffiths%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20be%20designed%20on%20a%20modular%20basis%20rather%20than%20based%20around%20terminals%20--%20meaning%20it%20can%20easily%20expand%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20stands%20to%20reason%20that%20Al%20Maktoum%20International%20has%20to%20be%20even%20bigger%20and%20even%20better%20(than%20Dubai%20International)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bairport%20of%20the%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20a%20project%20that%20extends%20way%20into%20the%202050s%2C%20because%20we%20take%20the%20long-term%20view%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20planning%20an%20airport%20that%20has%20terminals.%20We're%20going%20to%20completely%20change%20the%20business%20model%20for%20airports%2C%20make%20them%20actually%20far%20more%20intimate%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20all%20the%20legacy%20processes%20that%20we've%20had%20to%20subject%20our%20customers%20to%2C%20for%20far%20too%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-01%2F40oe4tn8_dubai-international-airportreuters-_625x300_29_January_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-impact-on-airports-dubai-plans-to-replace-worlds-busiest-airport-with-even-bigger-one-4575781%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dubai%20is%20forging%20ahead%20with%20plans%20to%20replace%20the%20world's%20busiest%20airport%20with%20an%20even%20bigger%20one%20as%20passenger%20traffic%20recovers%20to%20outstrip%20pre-pandemic%20levels%2C%20a%20top%20official%20told%20AFP%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-impact-on-airports-dubai-plans-to-replace-worlds-busiest-airport-with-even-bigger-one-4575781%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-impact-on-airports-dubai-plans-to-replace-worlds-busiest-airport-with-even-bigger-one-4575781%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-impact-on-airports-dubai-plans-to-replace-worlds-busiest-airport-with-even-bigger-one-4575781%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20a%20bartender%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%20Here%20are%20the%20techniques%20I%20used%20to%20land%20bigger%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20people%20I%20tried%20to%20avoid%20serving.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20bartender%20pours%20a%20drink%5C%22%2