Technology%2C%20I%20continued%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-bartenders-do-job-skills-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebartending%3C%2Fa%3E%20career%20in%20Atlanta.%20I%20eventually%20transitioned%20out%20of%20hospitality%20and%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffronthouz.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eplatform%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20provides%20venues%20with%20experienced%2C%20pretrained%20industry%20professionals%20on%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20my%20nine%20years%20as%20a%20bartender%2C%20I%20regularly%20found%20myself%20earning%20more%20tips%20than%20anyone%20else%20on%20my%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20techniques%20bartenders%20can%20use%20to%20earn%20bigger%20tips%20and%20ways%20to%20determine%20who%20will%20be%20a%20good%20tipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Show%20guests%20how%20much%20work%20goes%20into%20making%20each%20cocktail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20guests%20order%20a%20cocktail%2C%20they%20don't%20always%20understand%20how%20much%20time%20and%20effort%20goes%20into%20making%20it.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fina-garten-espresso-martini-taste-test-review-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eespresso%20martini%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20take%20around%20five%20minutes%20to%20make%2C%20for%20example.%20Other%20cocktails%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-cocktails-you-should-be-drinking-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERamos%20gin%20fizz%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20be%20quite%20labor-intensive%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20would%20make%20a%20drink%2C%20I'd%20always%20try%20to%20craft%20it%20directly%20in%20front%20of%20the%20guest%2C%20maintaining%20both%20conversation%20and%20eye%20contact.%20I%20also%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20drink%20visual%20and%20add%20a%20little%20flair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20be%20playful%20with%20the%20way%20you%20hold%20your%20bottles%2C%20pour%20the%20ingredients%2C%20ice%20the%20tins%2C%20garnish%20the%20drink%2C%20and%20place%20the%20beverage%20napkin%20before%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20guest%20sees%20that%20you%20care%20about%20what%20you're%20giving%20them%2C%20they're%20likely%20to%20tip%20more%20than%20they%20normally%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Treat%20regulars%20like%20they're%20good%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20remember%20regulars'%20names%2C%20stories%2C%20and%20drink%20orders.%20People%20want%20to%20feel%20remembered%2C%20understood%2C%20and%20appreciated.%20If%20you%20make%20them%20feel%20special%2C%20they'll%20want%20to%20make%20you%20feel%20special%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenuine%20connections%20and%20compliments%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way.%20Surface-level%20compliments%20are%20devoid%20of%20meaning%2C%20and%20guests%20will%20feel%20like%20you're%20trying%20to%20schmooze%20your%20way%20to%20a%20higher%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20a%20sincere%20interest%20in%20getting%20to%20know%20regular%20customers.%20It%20was%20my%20favorite%20thing%20when%20a%20guest%20returned%20and%20I%20already%20had%20something%20to%20talk%20about%20with%20them.%20This%20is%20another%20way%20to%20make%20the%20guest%20feel%20special%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20the%20bill%20comes%2C%20they'll%20feel%20obligated%20to%20leave%20a%20larger%20tip%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Recommend%20additional%20foods%20and%20beverages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20guest%20would%20sit%20at%20the%20bar%20and%20only%20order%20a%20beverage%2C%20I%20would%20suggest%20food%20items%20that%20paired%20well%20with%20their%20drink.%20That%20way%2C%20their%20bill%20would%20be%20higher%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20would%20the%20tip%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBartenders%20are%20expected%20to%20understand%20both%20the%20food%20and%20the%20beverage%20menus%2C%20and%20I%20used%20this%20knowledge%20to%20elevate%20the%20guests'%20overall%20experience.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20pair%20a%20spicy%20appetizer%20with%20a%20spicy%20drink%2C%20as%20it%20might%20be%20too%20much%20for%20someone's%20taste%20buds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Tell%20stories%20about%20the%20drinks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20often%20make%20classic%20cocktails%20at%20work%2C%20brush%20up%20on%20their%20history%20and%20try%20to%20tell%20the%20cocktail's%20story%20as%20you%20craft%20it.%20Two%20favorites%20of%20mine%20are%20the%20World%20War%20I%20history%20that%20inspired%20the%20original%20French%2075%20and%20the%20connection%20between%20the%20blend%20of%20ingredients%20in%20the%20Vieux%20Carr%C3%A9%20and%20the%20blend%20of%20cultures%20in%201930s%20New%20Orleans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20sure%20to%20follow%20trends%20to%20see%20which%20cocktails%20to%20highlight%20as%20you%20make%20them.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fnegroni-sbagliato%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENegroni%20sbagliato%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20historic%20cocktail%20that%20became%20super%20trendy%20with%20bar%20guests%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20lore%20behind%20people's%20drinks%20makes%20them%20feel%20connected%20to%20a%20bigger%20piece%20of%20history%2C%20and%20they%20might%20feel%20more%20inclined%20to%20tip%20based%20on%20the%20experience%20they%20had%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Identify%20who%20may%20be%20a%20good%20tipper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERegulars%20tend%20to%20earn%20their%20status%20after%20bartenders%20recognize%20them%20for%20being%20good%20tippers%20and%20reward%20them%20with%20special%20treatment%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20reasonable%20expectation%20that%20their%20tip%20will%20consistently%20be%2020%25%20or%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraft-cocktail%20enthusiasts%20are%20also%20pretty%20dependable%20for%20good%20tips%2C%20as%20they%20understand%20the%20level%20of%20craftsmanship%20and%20knowledge%20that%20goes%20into%20making%20their%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECouples%20in%20the%20preliminary%20stages%20of%20dating%20usually%20want%20to%20appear%20generous%20in%20front%20of%20their%20date.%20It's%20pretty%20standard%20to%20receive%20a%2020%25%20tip%20from%20whoever%20pays%20for%20the%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20clientele%20typically%20leave%2020%25.%20If%20they're%20networking%2C%20they'll%20be%20laser-focused%20on%20work%20and%20will%20appreciate%20your%20allowing%20them%20to%20do%20so.%20If%20they're%20freshly%20off%20the%20clock%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20suggest%20taking%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20who%20are%20particularly%20flashy%20and%20wear%20excessive%20designer%20items%20tend%20to%20be%20unpredictable%20with%20their%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20could%20choose%20one%20type%20of%20guest%20to%20sit%20at%20my%20bar%2C%20it%20would%20be%20other%20bartenders.%20Other%20hospitality-industry%20workers%20instantly%20feel%20like%20they're%20part%20of%20my%20family.%20Because%20of%20this%20deep%20connection%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20tip%20a%20disproportionate%20amount%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20upwards%20of%2040%25%20and%20sometimes%20even%20more%20than%20100%25.%20Though%20that%20may%20come%20at%20the%20price%20of%20a%20free%20shot%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Be%20wary%20of%20large%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETry%20to%20avoid%20serving%20people%20in%20large%20groups%20who%20seem%20to%20not%20know%20who's%20paying.%20Bars%20are%20loud%2C%20and%20space%20is%20limited%20%E2%80%94%20so%20unless%20drink%20orders%20were%20predetermined%2C%20large%20groups%20won't%20be%20well%20coordinated%20with%20their%20orders.%20This%20becomes%20extra%20complicated%20when%20it's%20time%20for%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20likely%20aftermath%20is%20that%20you'll%20be%20forced%20to%20split%20the%20check%2015%20ways%2C%20and%20the%20sum%20of%20their%20tips%20will%20be%20less%20than%2020%25.%20Or%20one%20person%20will%20end%20up%20paying%20and%20will%20be%20hesitant%20to%20leave%20a%20proper%20tip%20out%20of%20confusion%20or%20fear%20that%20they%20won't%20be%20paid%20back%20by%20the%20other%20members%20of%20their%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20serving%20a%20group%2C%20establish%20who's%20on%20each%20tab%20before%20making%20any%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-bigger-tips-bartender-who-avoid-serving-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65527c64385143459e8c2017%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-bigger-tips-bartender-who-avoid-serving-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Starr%20Douglas%20says%20showing%20guests%20how%20much%20work%20goes%20into%20making%20a%20cocktail%20and%20sharing%20the%20history%20behind%20the%20drink%20are%20great%20ways%20to%20earn%20a%20higher%20tip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-bigger-tips-bartender-who-avoid-serving-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JPMorgan%20boss%20Jamie%20Dimon%20warns%20it's%20too%20early%20for%20a%20Fed%20victory%20lap%2C%20as%20inflation%20'may%20not%20go%20away%20that%20quickly'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Dimon%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20speaks%20at%20the%20Economic%20Club%20of%20Washington%20September%2012%2C%202016%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20Dimon%20joined%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20state%20of%20U.S.%2C%20global%20and%