ive%20tightening%20is%20kicking%20in%2C%20but%20I%20still%20think%20you%20should%20be%20prepared%20that%20they%20might%20have%20to%20do%20a%20little%20bit%20more%2C%20just%20as%20a%20risk%20management%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20afraid%20inflation%20may%20not%20go%20away%20that%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JPMorgan%20boss%20isn't%20the%20only%20big%20name%20on%20Wall%20Street%20telling%20markets%20not%20to%20put%20too%20much%20stock%20in%20Tuesday's%20CPI%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Citadel%20founder%20Ken%20Griffin%20also%20flagged%20the%20risk%20that%20inflation%20stays%20sticky%20Tuesday%2C%20telling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-11-14%2Fgriffin-says-fed-s-credibility-at-risk-if-it-cuts-rates-too-soon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20only%20retain%20its%20credibility%20if%20it%20puts%20across%20%26quot%3Bthe%20message%20that%20they%20will%20put%20the%20inflation%20genie%20back%20in%20the%20bottle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-ceo-jamie-dimon-federal-reserve-interest-rates-inflation-cpi-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e4b79727e5db0018eedccc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-ceo-jamie-dimon-federal-reserve-interest-rates-inflation-cpi-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tuesday's%20softer-than-expected%20inflation%20number%20sparked%20a%20stock-market%20rally%2C%20with%20the%20benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20jumping%202%25%20in%20a%20single%20session.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gglover%40insider.com%20(George%20Glover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-ceo-jamie-dimon-federal-reserve-interest-rates-inflation-cpi-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Activist's%20Case%20Against%20Telegram%2C%20Paytm%20For%20Enabling%20Child%20Sex%20Abuse%20Content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHyderabad-based%20child%20rights%20activist%20Sunitha%20Krishnan%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20and%20digital%20payment%20apps%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20for%20allegedly%20abetting%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20child%20sex%20abuse%20material%2C%20or%20CSAM%2C%20and%20building%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20allows%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20called%20on%20the%20popular%20digital%20platforms%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20CSAM%20via%20their%20networks%2C%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20what%20protocols%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20distribution%20and%20sale%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20material%20involving%20children%2C%20including%20adult%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20tech%20platforms%20for%20%26quot%3Bmindfully%20(and)%20wilfully%26quot%3B%20aiding%20in%20the%20spread%20of%20CSAM%20and%20has%20demanded%20they%20%26quot%3Bbe%20aware%20where%20(and%20how)%20they%20are%20earning%20their%20money%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Paytm%2C%20PhonePe%2C%20nor%20Telegram%2C%20have%20responded%2C%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelegram%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20IM%2C%20or%20instant%20messaging%2C%20apps%20with%20700%20million%20users%20worldwide%3B%20India%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Russia%20are%20its%20biggest%20markets.%20The%20app%20offers%20extensive%20security%20features%2C%20including%20end-to-end%20encryption%2C%20private%20channels%20and%20self-destructing%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Prajwala%20-%20a%20NGO%20that%20combats%20sex%20trafficking%20-%20said%20she%20had%20been%20following%20a%20casual%20lead%20when%20she%20was%20shocked%20at%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20find%20CSAM%20online.%20She%20was%20also%20shocked%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20people%20illegally%20buying%20and%20selling%20videos%20of%20sex%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20were%20performed%2C%20she%20suspects%2C%20by%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%2C%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202016%2C%20said%20she%20chose%20to%20file%20the%20complaint%20on%20Tuesday%20because%20it%20was%20Children's%20Day%2C%20and%20because%20she%20wanted%20to%20red-flag%20dangers%20they%20face%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Investigation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20had%20been%20told%20of%20some%20Telegram%20accounts%20circulating%20CSAM.%20She%20downloaded%20the%20app%20at%20her%20office%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20posed%20as%20a%20buyer.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20verification%20(to%20establish%20the%20name)%20and%20I%20could%20name%20myself%20under%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20which%20I%20chose%20as%20Vashisht%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20explained%20the%20Telegram%20app%20has%20a%20search%20bar%20on%20the%20home%20page%20that%20lets%20you%20find%20groups%2Fcontent%2Fpeople%20with%20certain%20keywords%20-%20much%20like%20Google.%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20across%20a%20group%20called%20'Girls%20and%20Boys%20Chatting'.%20...%20on%20entering%20the%20group%2C%20which%20had%2031%2C000%20members%2C%20I%20found%20a%20stream%20of%20messages%20(selling)%20different%20categories%20of%20explicit%20material%2C%20including%20CSAM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20encryption%20features%20sometimes%20don't%20allow%20screenshots.%20The%20self-destruct%20feature%20of%20Telegram%20gives%20operators%20anonymity%20and%20safety%20from%20being%20tracked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20private%20channels%20allow%20the%20admin%20to%20admit%20and%20remove%20members%20and%20not%20be%20visible%20in%20general%20search%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20established%20contact%20with%20three%20sellers%20for%20CSAM%2C%20and%20made%20payments%20via%20the%20Paytm%20or%20PhonePe%20app%20in%20each%20case.%20From%20one%20seller%20she%20found%20CSAM%20for%20Rs%2050%20and%20purchased%20more%20links%20after%20negotiating%20the%20amount%20from%20Rs%20400%20to%20Rs%20150.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20asked%20why%20there%20was%20a%20delay%20after%20payment%2C%20the%20seller%20said%20he%20had%20gone%20for%20tuitions.%20That%20is%20when%20I%20realised%20this%20is%20a%20minor%20I%20am%20dealing%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSAM%20delivered%20contained%20scenes%20of%20oral%20sex%20and%20intercourse%20with%20children%2C%20solo%20streaming%20of%20children%20between%20three%20and%2012%20years%20of%20age%20as%20well%20as%20adult%20pornography.%20%26quot%3BIt%20also%20contained%20videos%20of%20(alleged)%20gang-rape%20(with)%20and%20molesters%20seeming%20to%20be%20from%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rs%20100%20(via%20PhonePe%20to%20the%20second)%2C%20she%20was%20given%20access%20to%20six%20private%20channels%20containing%20explicit%20material.%20From%20a%20third%2C%20on%20payment%20of%20Rs%2050%20(also%20PhonePe)%2C%20she%20got%20access%20to%20CSAM%20links%2C%20including%20adults%20participating%20in%20intercourse%20with%20children%20and%20self-streaming%20by%20underage%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20said%20she%20came%20across%20groups%20with%20as%20many%20as%2040%2C000%20members%3B%20528%20were%20online%20at%20one%20time.%20The%20seller%20on%20one%20group%20offered%20access%20to%20his%20private%20channel%20through%20links%20upon%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20payment%2C%20the%20seller%20gave%20her%20access%20to%20a%20channel%20called%20'desi%20videos'%20that%20contained%20adult%20pornography.%20After%20she%20complained%2C%20he%20gave%20her%20access%20to%20a%20channel%20named%20'Heart%204'.%20She%20paid%20Rs%2080%20more%20and%20got%20access%20to%20a%20'Heart2'%20channel%20that%20contained%20more%20CSAM%2C%20including%20pictures%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Warning%20From%20Telegram%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20this%20entire%20exercise%2C%20not%20a%20single%20pop-up%20appeared%20on%20Telegram%2C%20warning%20that%20dissemination%20of%20child%20sexually%20abusive%20material%20is%20a%20criminal%20offence%20and%20not%20reporting%20the%20same%20may%20attract%20POCSO%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20arguing%20Telegram%20is%20therefore%20facilitating%20sale%20and%20purchase%20of%20CSAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20not%20verifying%20identities%2C%20she%20added%2C%20Telegram%20is%20allowing%20those%20engaged%20in%20distribution%20to%20conceal%20their%20names.%20And%20Telegram's%20end-to-end%20encryption%20allows%20transactions%20to%20purchase%20such%20material.%20Encryption%20settings%20allow%20prevention%20of%20screenshots%2C%20copying%20of%20links%20and%20collection%20of%20any%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20providing%20QR%20access%20to%20such%20sellers%20to%20distribute%20such%20material%20at%20extremely%20low%20costs%20with%20ease%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20has%20complained%20to%20Telangana%20DGP%20Anjani%20Kumar%20and%20intends%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCirculation%20of%20such%20sexually%20exploitative%20content%20of%20children%20threatens%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20all%20children%20and%20are%20grievous%20criminal%20offenses.%20Demand%20for%20CSAM%20will%20accelerate%20child%20trafficking%20for%20sexual%20exploitation.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20few%20players%20I%20randomly%20came%20across.%20Immediate%20and%20urgent%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20Telegram%2C%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20so%20as%20to%20prevent%20any%20more%20children%20being%20sexually%20exploited...%26quot%3B%20she%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fchild-abuse-istock-650_650x400_51460717509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hyderabad-based%20child%20rights%20activist%20Sunitha%20Krishnan%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20and%20digital%20payment%20apps%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20for%20allegedly%20abetting%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20child%20sex%20abuse%20material%2C%20or%20CSAM.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinod%20Adani%20Among%2066%20Indians%20Who%20Got%20Cyprus%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Passport%E2%80%99%20Between%202014%20and%202020%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15150641%2Fimage-1504.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBetween%202014%20and%202020%2C%2066%20Indians%20managed%20to%20obtain%20Cyprus%20passports%20within%20three%20months%20to%20a%20year%2C%20under%20the%20tax%20haven%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20scheme%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20International%20Consortium%20of%20Investigative%20Journalists%20(ICIJ)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fvinod-adani-pankaj-oswal-among-66-indians-who-got-golden-passport-9026977%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20part%20of%20Cyprus%20Confidential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fsecrecy-and-no-tax-reason-why-indians-look-at-cyprus-9027035%2F%5C%22%3ECyprus%20Confidential%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20worldwide%20offshore%20probe%20of%203.6%20million%20documents%20in%20English%20and%20Greek%2C%20exposing%20a%20trail%20of%20companies%20established%20in%20Cyprus%20as%20a%20tax%20haven%20by%20global%20elites%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fcracking-cyprus-confidential-eu-state-gave-investors-tax-haven-secrecy-and-a-golden-passport-9026642%2F%5C%22%3ERussian%20oligarchs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CCyprus%20Investment%20Programme%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20scheme%20was%20launched%20in%202007.%20It%20enabled%20financially%20prominent%20individuals%20to%20obtain%20Cypriot%20citizenship%2C%20thereby%20attracting%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2066%20Indians%20who%20got%20their%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-gautam-adani-u-turn%5C%22%3EVinod%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20who%20came%20under%20spotlight%20in%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20investigation%3B%20Pankaj%20Oswal%2C%20chairman%20and%20founder%20of%20Burrup%20Holdings%20Limited%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20baron%20Surendra%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20European%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20Cyprus%20repealed%20its%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20scheme%20and%20stopped%20receiving%20new%20applications%20on%20November%201%2C%202020.%20However%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20process%20pending%20applications.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20European%20Commission%20decided%20to%20send%20a%20reasoned%20opinion%20to%20Cyprus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Finf_21_2743%5C%22%3EJune%209%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20then%2C%20Cyprus%20stopped%20processing%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20scrapped%20due%20to%20alleged%20misuse%20and%20for%20allowing%20persons%20with%20criminal%20charges%2C%20dubious%20character%20and%20PEPs%20(politically%20exposed%20persons)%20to%20acquire%20Cyprus%20passports%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENames%20of%20a%20total%20of%2083%20individuals%20were%20flagged%20for%20review%20and%20possible%20revocation.%20A%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20earlier%20citizens%20of%20Russia%20and%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%2C%20most%20were%20marked%20for%20applications%20bearing%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20statement%20by%20the%20investors%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Commission%20appointed%20by%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20Cyprus%2C%20Georgios%20Savvides%2C%20in%20September%202020%20and%20headed%20by%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20Chairman%2C%20Myron%20Nicolatos%2C%20made%20the%20list%20of%20these%20possible%20revocations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Cyprus%20government%20has%20not%20yet%20officially%20revealed%20how%20many%20of%20those%20under%20the%20scanner%20had%20their%20Cypriot%20citizenships%20revoked%2C%20the%20daily%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevocations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20Indian%20on%20the%20list%20of%20proposed%20revocations%20of%20Cypriot%20passports%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fnsel-case-ed-attaches-defaulters-property-in-dubai%2Farticle65523301.ece%5C%22%3EAnubhav%20Aggarwal%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20businessman%20whose%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20was%20approved%20within%20four%20months%20on%20November%202%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nicolatos%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20report%20states%20that%20Aggarwal%20was%20implicated%20in%20the%20National%20Spot%20Exchange%20Limited%20(NSEL)%20scam%20and%20that%20he%20failed%20to%20mention%20his%20links%20with%20the%20suspect%20companies%20in%20his%20application%20for%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20accused%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Rs%203%2C600%20crore%20NSEL%20scam%2C%20Aggarwal%20faced%20arrest%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20in%20August%202020.%20In%20June%202020%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20seized%20his%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAggarwal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20Indian%20obtaining%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20under%20the%20now-defunct%20investment%20scheme%2C%20despite%20legal%20issues%20with%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENesamanimaran%20Muthu%2C%20better%20known%20as%20MGM%20Maran%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20businessman%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Mercantile%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20acquired%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20in%202016.%20His%20application%20was%20cleared%20in%20just%20two%20months.%20In%202017%2C%20his%20two%20children%20also%20got%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20the%20ED%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfsi.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fed-attaches-assets-worth-rs-205-36-cr-of-chennai-based-firm%2F96538226%5C%22%3Eattached%3C%2Fa%3E%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20200%20crores%20of%20his%20Maran%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20Agrifurane%20Industries%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20probe%20agency%20had%20issued%20a%20media%20release%20saying%20that%20assets%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20293%20crore%20had%20been%20attached%20by%20them%20since%20an%20equivalent%20foreign%20investment%20had%20been%20made%20by%20Maran%20in%20two%20companies%20in%20Singapore%20without%20approval%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20mentioned%20Maran%E2%80%99s%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20in%20an%20official%20release.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20escape%20the%20reach%20of%20Indian%20laws%2C%20MGM%20Maran%20surrendered%20his%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20it%20was%20also%20found%20that%20MGM%20Maran%20also%20started%20transferring%20his%20wealth%20from%20India%20to%20overseas%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20same%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20the%20Indian%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20overseas%20direct%20investments%20from%20Southern%20Agrifurane%20Industries%20Private%20Limited%20(his%20flagship%20company)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ED%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Cyprus%20Confidential%20investigation%20by%20OCCRP%20and%20other%20media%20partners%2C%20the%20Cyprus%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20said%20that%20they%20have%20decided%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20deprivation%20of%20citizenship%20of%20233%20individuals%20and%20of%20them%2C%2068%20individuals%20are%20investors%20and%20165%20are%20family%20members%20of%20the%20investors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20over%20tax%20evasion%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20January%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3EHindenburg%20Research%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailed%20Vinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20offshore%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%2C%20which%20included%20downloading%20and%20cataloguing%20the%20entire%20Mauritius%20corporate%20registry%2C%20uncovered%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20through%20several%20close%20associates%2C%20manages%20a%20vast%20labyrinth%20of%20offshore%20shell%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20it%20identified%2038%20Mauritius%20shell%20entities%20controlled%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20or%20close%20associates.%20It%20also%20identified%20entities%20that%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Csurreptitiously%20controlled%E2%80%9D%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20several%20Caribbean%20Islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20these%20shell%20companies%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20per%20the%20report%2C%20was%20key%20in%20managing%20%E2%80%9Ca%20vast%20labyrinth%20of%20offshore%20shell%20entities%E2%80%9D%20to%20facilitate%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manipulation%2C%20it%20said%2C%20was%20helping%20the%20Adani%20companies%20maintain%20their%20appearance%20of%20financial%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany%2Fcorporate-trends%2Fadani-addresses-hindenburg-allegations-head-on-at-agm-says-vested-interests-wrote-report-to-hurt-company%2Farticleshow%2F101845922.cms%5C%22%3Ehas%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20these%20allegations%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccalculated%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20the%20independence%2C%20integrity%20and%20quality%20of%20Indian%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20growth%20story%20and%20ambition%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20who%20mostly%20occupied%20the%20back%20seat%20in%20business%20operations%20of%20Adani%20Group%2C%20came%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-gautam-adani-u-turn%5C%22%3Esaid%3