%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20cited%20that%20in%202020%20there%20were%20around%20180%2C000%20private%20education%20institutions%20nationwide%20which%20accounted%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20all%20education%20institutions%20in%20China.%20These%20schools%20had%2055.6%20million%20students'%20enrollment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20international%20schools%2C%20which%20can%20only%20enroll%20students%20with%20foreign%20passports%2C%20have%20mostly%20seen%20student%20numbers%20decline%20due%20to%20expatriates%20from%20countries%20leaving%20after%20the%20pandemic%20and%20amid%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20schools%20prior%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20drove%20a%20surge%20of%20privately%20run%20bilingual%20schools%20in%20China%20offering%20a%20western%20exam%20curriculum.%20The%20business%20stumbled%20later%20as%20Beijing%20imposed%20new%20rules%20in%202021%20and%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20private%20tutoring%20business%2C%20aimed%20at%20easing%20pressure%20on%20children%20and%20lowering%20family%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Reuters%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20enrollments%20in%20Indian%20schools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20per%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20report%2C%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20primary%20schools%20across%20many%20states%20in%20India%20have%20an%20enrolment%20of%20less%20than%2060.%20The%20cost%20of%20such%20sub-scale%20schools%20in%20the%20form%20of%20extensive%20multi-grade%20teaching%2C%20lack%20of%20a%20student%20and%20parent%20community%20that%20can%20demand%20account%20ability%2C%20poor%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20same%201-2%20teachers%20also%20handling%20all%20administrative%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20headmasters%2F%20principals%2C%20etc%20is%20very%20high.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20report%20suggested%20school%20mergers%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20addressing%20the%20lack%20%C2%A0of%20enrollments%