%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20office%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20bus%20accident%20in%20Doda%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20distressing.%20My%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20near%20and%20dear%20ones.%20I%20pray%20that%20the%20injured%20recover%20at%20the%20earliest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20bus%20accident%20in%20Doda%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20distressing.%20My%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20near%20and%20dear%20ones.%20I%20pray%20that%20the%20injured%20recover%20at%20the%20earliest.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20ex-gratia%20of%20Rs.%202%20lakh%20from%20PMNRF%20would%20be%20given%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20each%20deceased.%20Rs.%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20PMO%20India%20(%40PMOIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPMOIndia%2Fstatus%2F1724705451554800072%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20that%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each%20would%20be%20given%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20accident.%20Those%20injured%20will%20receive%20an%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700041020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fggnvvh3c_doda-jammu-bus-accident_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoda-bus-accident-several-killed-as-bus-plunges-into-gorge-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-doda-4575513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirty-six%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20after%20a%20bus%20fell%20into%20a%20gorge%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Doda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%