h-impunity-un-expert-says%2Farticleshow%2F105232814.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105232814.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20United%20Nations%20expert%20has%20called%20on%20the%20Philippines%20to%20disband%20its%20anti-communist%20task%20force%2C%20citing%20concerns%20over%20human%20rights%20abuses.%20UN%20Special%20Rapporteur%20Ian%20Fry%20urged%20for%20an%20independent%20investigation%20into%20the%20National%20Task%20Force%20to%20End%20Local%20Communist%20Armed%20Conflict%20(NTF-ELCAC)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Bred-tagging%26quot%3B%20and%20arbitrary%20arrests.%20The%20task%20force%2C%20chaired%20by%20President%20Rodrigo%20Duterte%2C%20denies%20these%20allegations.%20Fry%20stated%20that%20the%20task%20force%20has%20exceeded%20its%20original%20mandate%20and%20should%20be%20replaced%20with%20a%20more%20effective%20approach%20to%20counterterrorism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-counter-insurgency-force-operating-with-impunity-un-expert-says%2Farticleshow%2F105232814.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-counter-insurgency-force-operating-with-impunity-un-expert-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F105232814.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-counter-insurgency-force-operating-with-impunity-un-expert-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F105232814.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20APEC%20And%20Why%20Is%20India%20Not%20A%20Member%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20attending%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20meeting%20in%20the%20United%20States%20today%2C%20which%20will%20also%20see%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Xi%20Jinping%20hold%20their%20second%20in-person%20dialogue%20since%20Mr%20Biden%20assumed%20office%20in%202021%2C%20amid%20tensions%20and%20a%20trust%20deficit%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20between%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20largest%20economies%20and%20two%20great%20military%20powers%20in%20the%20world%20would%20be%20significant%20at%20any%20point%2C%20but%20it%20assumes%20even%20more%20importance%20now%20as%20there%20are%20two%20polarising%20wars%20going%20on%20-%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20and%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20-%20and%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20has%20taken%20a%20hit%20because%20of%20the%20Taiwan%20issue%2C%20trade%20tensions%20and%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAPEC%20Formation%2C%20Membership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormed%20in%201989%2C%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20grouping%20has%2021%20members%2C%20but%20India%20is%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20It%20had%20made%20a%20request%20to%20join%20the%20grouping%20in%201991%2C%20the%20year%20which%20saw%20the%20introduction%20of%20liberalisation%20and%20entirely%20changed%20the%20shape%20and%20trajectory%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy.%20%C2%A0While%20a%20majority%20of%20members%20are%20in%20favour%20of%20India's%20inclusion%2C%20some%20have%20opposed%20it%2C%20citing%20the%20country's%20record%20on%20economic%20reforms%20and%20claiming%20that%20it%20has'%20protectionist%20instincts'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20India%20not%20being%20included%20in%20the%20grouping%20was%20a%20membership%20freeze%2C%20which%20was%20in%20force%20since%201997%20but%20was%20not%20extended%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20members%20of%20the%20grouping%20are%20Australia%2C%20Brunei%2C%20Hong%20Kong%20(which%20the%20APEC%20website%20refers%20to%20as%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20China)%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Russia%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Peru%2C%20Chile%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Chinese%20Taipei%20(Taiwan).%20The%20grouping's%20focus%20is%20on%20economies%2C%20rather%20than%20countries%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20which%20China%20claims%20as%20its%20own%2C%20participate%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20APEC%20accounts%20for%20about%2062%25%20of%20global%20GDP%20and%20almost%20half%20of%20global%20trade.%20It%20operates%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20non-binding%20commitments%20with%20decisions%20reached%20by%20consensus%20and%20commitments%20undertaken%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAims%20This%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20APEC%20Economic%20Leaders'%20Week%20is%20being%20held%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20According%20to%20the%20Reuters%20report%2C%20the%20US%20has%20chosen%20the%20theme%20%26quot%3BCreating%20a%20Resilient%20and%20Sustainable%20Future%20for%20All%26quot%3B%20for%20APEC%202023.%20It%20says%20it%20aims%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Binterconnected%2C%20innovative%2C%20and%20inclusive%26quot%3B%20region%20and%20%26quot%3Bto%20advance%20a%20free%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20open%20economic%20policy%20agenda%20that%20benefits%20US%20workers%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202021%2C%20APEC%20members%20made%20up%20seven%20of%20the%20United%20States'%20top%2010%20overall%20trading%20partners%20and%20Washington%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20up%20the%20relative%20strength%20of%20its%20economy%20in%20challenging%20times%20-%20a%20veiled%20comparison%20with%20difficulties%20China%20has%20faced%20after%20years%20of%20spectacular%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20asked%20ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%20what%20he%20expected%20to%20achieve%20during%20his%20dialogue%20with%20Mr%20Jinping%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20back%20on%20a%20normal%20course%20of%20corresponding%3B%20being%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20talk%20to%20one%20another%20if%20there's%20a%20crisis%3B%20being%20able%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20(militaries)%20still%20have%20contact%20with%20one%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20key%20leaders%20at%20the%20meeting%20will%20be%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20and%20Indonesian%20President%20Joko%20Widodo.%20Russia%20will%20be%20represented%20by%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Alexei%20Overchuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700040540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fnl0te4c4_biden-xi-650_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-xi-biden-meet-ndtv-explains-what-is-apec-and-why-india-is-not-a-member-4575536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20attending%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20meeting%20in%20the%20United%20States%20today%2C%20which%20will%20also%20see%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Xi%20Jinping%20hold%20their%20second%20in-person%20dialogue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-xi-biden-meet-ndtv-explains-what-is-apec-and-why-india-is-not-a-member-4575536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-xi-biden-meet-ndtv-explains-what-is-apec-and-why-india-is-not-a-member-4575536%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-xi-biden-meet-ndtv-explains-what-is-apec-and-why-india-is-not-a-member-4575536%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SA%20rugby%20office%20burglars%20tou