%20hoc%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20P%20S%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20and%20Justice%20T%20G%20Shivashankare%20Gowda%20noted%20in%20their%20recent%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETS%20Rajan%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20late%20TK%20Sheshadri%20Iyengar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Rajajingar%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20approached%20the%20High%20Court%20in%202021%20with%20a%20writ%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20was%20working%20as%20a%20'Patel'%20in%20Thangali%20village%2C%20Kadur%20Taluk%2C%20Chikkamagaluru%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20high%20court%20and%20upheld%20in%20an%20appeal%20(1997)%20subsequently%2C%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Patel's%20Sangha%20was%20allowed%20and%20Mr%20Rajan's%20father%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20specified%20a%20compassionate%20allowance%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20month%20from%20August%201979%20to%20June%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rajan's%20father%20filed%20several%20applications%20and%20representations%20for%20the%20allowance%20but%20it%20was%20not%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20father's%20death%2C%20Mr%20Rajan%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20Tahsildar%20of%20Kadur%20requesting%20for%20the%20payment.%20It%20was%20rejected%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rajan%20then%20approached%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Administrative%20Tribunal%2C%20which%20also%20rejected%20his%20application%2C%20following%20which%20he%20approached%20the%20HC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tahsildar%20had%20rejected%20the%20request%20made%20by%20the%20petitioner%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20his%20father%20had%20not%20received%20ad%20hoc%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rajan's%20advocate%20argued%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20such%20an%20endorsement%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20is%20unsustainable%20in%20law%20because%20it%20was%20for%20the%20government%20to%20sanction%20and%20release%20the%20ad%20hoc%20allowance%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20in%20its%20judgement%20rejected%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20State%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20contention%20urged%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20State%20Government%20that%20since%20the%20petitioner%20has%20not%20been%20granted%20the%20ad%20hoc%20compensation%20and%20therefore%2C%20he%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20claim%20the%20arrears%20is%20rather%20surprising.%20We%20may%20record%20that%20it%20is%20not%20disputed%20by%20the%20government%20that%20the%20petitioner's%20father%20was%20working%20as%20Patel%20of%20Village%20Thangali.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20rejected%20the%20Tahsildar's%20endorsement%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%2C%20there%20is%20no%20dispute%20that%20petitioner's%20father%20was%20working%20as%20Village%20Officer%20of%20Thangali%20Village%2C%20State%20ought%20to%20have%20considered%20the%20claim%20for%20arrears.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20same%2C%20the%20reason%20recorded%20by%20the%20Tahsildar%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20arrears%20as%20his%20father%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20ad%20hoc%20allowance%20is%20wholly%20untenable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20ordered%20that%20the%20State%20should%20calculate%20and%20pay%20the%20arrears%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ad%20hoc%20allowance%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%20100%20between%201979%20and%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20allowance%20and%20arrears%20from%201990%20to%201994%20should%20be%20paid%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%20500%20per%20month%2C%20the%20HC%20said.%20It%20also%20ordered%20a%20simple%20interest%20of%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20amount%20from%20the%20date%20of%20entitlement.%20The%20payment%20is%20to%20be%20made%20within%20three%20months%2C%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20p