0of%20children%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savethechildren.net%2Fnews%2Fgaza-3195-children-killed-three-weeks-surpasses-annual-number-children-killed-conflict-zones%5C%22%3Ekilled%20annually%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20all%20other%20conflicts%20since%202019.%20The%20awful%20statistic%20led%20to%20United%20Nations%20Secretary%20General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20calling%20Gaza%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fnov%2F06%2Fgaza-becoming-a-graveyard-for-children-says-un-secretary-general%5C%22%3Egraveyard%20for%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20has%20been%20unprecedented%20in%20scale%20and%20scope.%20While%20not%20as%20acute%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-flash-update-31-enarhe%5C%22%3EEast%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20impact%20on%20young%20people%20in%20those%20territories%20has%20also%20been%20severe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20schools%20have%20been%20shut%20due%20to%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20movement%20between%20towns%20is%20significantly%20limited.%20Violence%20between%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20has%20increased%2C%20with%20little%20apparent%20intervention%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20or%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicefusa.org%2Fstories%2Fchildren-trapped-gaza-conflict-face-generational-trauma%5C%22%3EUNICEF%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20the%20recent%20escalation%20could%20lead%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctrauma%20which%20could%20last%20a%20lifetime%E2%80%9D%20for%20children%20in%20both%20Palestine%20and%20Israel.%20Even%20before%20this%20crisis%2C%20however%2C%20the%20toll%20of%20the%20protracted%20conflict%20on%20Palestinian%20children%20has%20been%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20four%20years%20between%202019%20and%202022%2C%20I%20led%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Flearning-margins-assessment-learner-and-educator-well-being-outcomes-midst-and-following-contagion-and-conflict-palestine-january-2023%5C%22%3Estudy%20exploring%20children%E2%80%99s%20wellbeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gaza%2C%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConducted%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Norwegian%20Refugee%20Council%2C%20we%20surveyed%20approximately%20800%20children%20and%20their%20teachers.%20The%20trends%20we%20observed%20were%20cause%20for%20grave%20concern%20%E2%80%93%20even%20before%20events%20of%20the%20past%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Insecure%20all%20the%20time%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20we%20surveyed%20in%20Gaza%20had%20lived%20through%20at%20least%20three%20large-scale%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20in%20their%20lifetimes.%20Due%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20longstanding%20blockade%20of%20the%20territory%2C%20they%20have%20grown%20up%20with%20food%20insecurity%20and%20unreliable%20supplies%20of%20electricity%20and%20drinking%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20most%20of%20their%20caregivers%20unemployed%2C%20many%20children%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20poor%20living%20conditions%2C%20as%20well%20as%20violence%20within%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20children%20of%20Gaza%20we%20surveyed%20in%202019%20showed%20tremendous%20resilience%3A%2080%25%20felt%20things%20would%20be%20better%20in%20the%20future.%20For%20many%2C%20attending%20and%20succeeding%20in%20school%20offered%20the%20hope%20of%20finding%20a%20way%20out%20of%20their%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20however%2C%20the%20situation%20had%20changed%20markedly.%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fafter-covid-19-and-the-latest-violence-what-now-for-the-school-children-of-palestine-161496%5C%22%3Emajor%20escalation%20in%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202021%20just%20as%20students%20returned%20to%20school%20full%20time%2C%20saw%20only%2020%25%20positive%20about%20their%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20circumstances%20had%20deflated%20their%20capacity%20to%20aspire%2C%20hope%20and%20dream%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%20As%20one%20group%20of%20boys%20described%20in%20a%20story%20they%20wrote%20together%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20remain%20afraid%20of%20the%20future%2C%20and%20not%20trusting%20it%20will%20bring%20us%20any%20more%20hope.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20forget%20the%20events%20we%20have%20been%20through%20and%20feel%20insecure%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPandemic%20respite%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20research%20suggests%20the%20same%20is%20true%20for%20children%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20which%20face%20the%20ongoing%20presence%20of%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20military%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20surveyed%20in%20the%20part%20of%20Hebron%20under%20Israeli%20military%20control%20(Hebron%20H2)%2C%20and%20in%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20face%20daily%20restrictions%20as%20they%20travel%20to%20and%20from%20school.%20Many%20need%20to%20pass%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warchildholland.org%2Fnews%2Feducation-threat-west-bank%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520West%2520Bank%2520education%2Cclasses%2520or%2520after%252Dschool%2520activities%5C%22%3Emilitary%20checkpoints%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20face%20delays%20and%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20children%2C%20the%20pandemic%20offered%20a%20kind%20of%20respite%20from%20having%20to%20make%20these%20daily%20journeys.%20One%20group%20of%20girls%20living%20in%20Hebron%20H2%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streets%20were%20calm%20and%20quiet%2C%20and%20there%20was%20not%20the%20usual%20conflict%20between%20us%20and%20the%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20reopened%20after%20the%20pandemic%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2F2022-among-deadliest-years-palestinians-west-bank-middle-east-peace-process-coordinator-tells-security-council%5C%22%3Etension%20and%20violence%20mounted%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20West%20Bank%20over%20the%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20Israeli%20settlements%20on%20seized%20Palestinian%20land.%20Attacks%20in%20and%20around%20schools%20increased%2C%20as%20did%20Palestinian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20most%20acutely%20affected%20areas%2C%20our%20survey%20recorded%20significant%20declines%20in%20children%E2%80%99s%20wellbeing%2C%20particularly%20in%20their%20ability%20to%20calm%20themselves%20when%20scared%2C%20and%20to%20think%20of%20solutions%20to%20daily%20challenges%20they%20faced.%20One%20group%20of%20girls%20at%20a%20school%20outside%20Jerusalem%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20there%20are%20incidences%2C%20we%20have%20strikes%20which%20close%20our%20school%20again%20and%20return%20us%20to%20learning%20from%20home%20which%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20like.%20We%20are%20frustrated%2C%20depressed%2C%20and%20%5Bmade%5D%20angry%20by%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrustration%20and%20escalation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressure%20is%20now%20mounting%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20to%20end%20this%20latest%20cycle%20of%20violence.%20If%20and%20when%20this%20happens%2C%20humanitarian%20organisations%20and%20donors%20will%20flood%20back%20in%20to%20restore%2C%20repair%20and%20attempt%20to%20remediate%20the%20physical%20and%20psychological%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20root%20causes%20and%20drivers%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20remain%20unaddressed%2C%20and%20if%20there%20is%20no%20greater%20international%20resolve%20to%20change%20the%20status%20quo%20once%20and%20for%20all%2C%20it%20seems%20inevitable%20we%20will%20witness%20more%20bloodshed%20and%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict%20deserve%20a%20durable%20and%20lasting%20solution.%20Our%20survey%20suggests%20their%20resilience%20was%20already%20seriously%20declining%20before%20the%20current%20emergency.%20Without%20hope%2C%20this%20will%20deteriorate%20even%20further.%20As%20one%20school%20principal%20told%20me%3A%20We%20feel%20trapped%20by%20the%20situation%20we%20are%20in%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20just%20escalates%20out%20of%20frustration.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F217535%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fritesh-shah-1235587%5C%22%3ERitesh%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Senior%20Lecturer%20in%20Education%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-auckland-1305%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Auckland%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwe-remain-afraid-of-the-future-how-palestinian-childrens-optimism-was-fading-even-before-this-crisis-217535%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700039448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14152710%2FPalestinian_children_on_rooftop.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-reports-more-child-deaths-than-all-