Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftmc-mp-mahua-moitra-criticise-government-parliamentary-speech)%5C%22%3E%20maiden%20parliamentary%20speech%20in%20June%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20president.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20%E2%80%98like%20her%E2%80%99%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20get%20accused%20of%20a%20several%20%E2%80%98crimes%E2%80%99%20almost%20immediately%20after%20stepping%20into%20public%20life.%20They%20are%20targeted%20because%20their%20presence%20upsets%20the%20patriarchal%20belief%20that%20only%20women%20conforming%20to%20social%20mores%20can%20be%20successful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20remains%20among%20the%20few%20Indian%20women%20to%20secure%20untrammelled%20power%2C%20but%2C%20she%20consolidated%20her%20hold%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Findira-gandhi-a-goongi-gudiya-who-went-on-to-become-iron-lady-1089668-2017-11-19%5C%22%3Epositioning%20herself%20as%20the%20only%20man%20in%20her%20cabinet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F684337%2Flok-sabha-ethics-committee-recommends-expulsion-of-tmc-mp-mahua-moitra-from-lok-sabha%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Over%20in%20Minutes%E2%80%99%3A%20Ethics%20Committee%20Recommends%20Expulsion%20of%20TMC%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20From%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%E2%80%99s%20party%20chief%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20despite%20her%20fiery%20capacities%20displayed%20over%20more%20than%20four%20decades%20in%20politics%2C%20remains%20the%20universal%20%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Even%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdidi-oh-didi-how-bjp-crafted-its-own-humiliation-in-bengal%5C%22%3Ewhen%20he%20infamously%20hurled%20that%20misogynous%20taunt%20at%20her%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20to%20inevitably%20use%20her%20moniker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20in%20contrast%2C%20did%20not%20%E2%80%98sanitise%E2%80%99%20her%20sexuality%2C%20never%20denied%20her%20relationship%20and%20had%20the%20gumption%20to%20label%20her%20primary%20accuser%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjilted%20ex%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20not%20surprising%20that%20her%20interrogation%20during%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20meeting%20was%20aimed%20at%20learning%20who%20she%20spoke%20with%20at%20night%20and%20if%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20wife%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20interactions%20with%20her.%20Ruling%20party%20members%20in%20this%20instance%2C%20men%20especially%2C%20behaved%20like%20typical%20male%20chauvinists%20unnerved%20by%20%E2%80%98independent%E2%80%99%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20counter%20women%2C%20they%20know%20just%20one%20trick%3A%20painting%20them%20as%20being%20of%20%E2%80%98easy%20virtue%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20BJP%20social%20media%20handles%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20circulating%20her%20pictures%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20in%20hand%20and%20also%20being%20arm%20in%20arm%20with%20a%20male%20political%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20acquiring%20a%20public%20image%2C%20Moitra%20was%20particularly%20susceptible%20to%20being%20targeted%20by%20misogynists%20because%20she%20had%20no%20family%20%E2%80%98shield%E2%80%99%3B%20a%20single%20woman%2C%20a%20divorced%20one%20at%20that%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20former%20spouse%20is%20non-Indian%2C%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20in%20exceptional%20cases%20can%20a%20woman%20with%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20personal%20background%20avoid%20presumptions%20about%20easy%20%E2%80%98availability%E2%80%99.%20Almost%20universally%2C%20only%20the%20virginal%20or%20the%20strictly%20monogamous-for-life%20are%20considered%20virtuous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F684557%2Fmahua-moitra-and-the-question-of-maryada%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20Question%20of%20Maryada%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20styling%2C%20grooming%2C%20penchant%20for%20branded%20clothing%2C%20and%20accessories%2C%20mirrored%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fashionable%20outfits%20and%20tastes.%20But%2C%20unlike%20him%2C%20she%20had%20no%20socially%20backward%20identity%20and%20economically%20underprivileged%20upbringing%20to%20flaunt.%20Furthermore%2C%20questions%20could%20be%20asked%20about%20her%20relationship%20status%20because%20of%20her%20gender%20identity.%20Similar%20posers%20are%20not%20put%20to%20male%20politicians%2C%20especially%20from%20Treasury%20Benches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20relative%20anonymity%20derived%20from%20association%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20youth%20brigade%20ended%20in%202010%2C%20and%20she%20switched%20sides%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20orchestrated%20attacks%20increased.%20With%20the%20Congress%20still%20in%20power%20and%20the%20BJP%20emerging%20as%20serious%20challenger%2C%20she%20got%20opportunities%20to%20showcase%20her%20skills%20at%20playing%20David%20while%20battling%20Goliaths%20in%20TV%20studios.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%20before%20successfully%20contesting%20the%202016%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20polls%2C%20she%20made%20a%20mark%2C%20courtesy%20her%20way%20with%20words%2C%20a%20bristly%20tongue%20that%20knew%20little%20restraint%2C%20and%20the%20aplomb%20to%20ask%20awkward%20questions%20to%20those%20in%20power.%20This%20drew%20sharp%20responses%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20BJP%20which%20emerged%20as%20TMC%E2%80%99%20principal%20opponent%20in%20the%20state.%20Much%20of%20the%20exasperation%20stemmed%20from%20her%20being%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20heated%20exchange%20thereafter%2C%20went%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%20The%20defamation%20suit%20she%20filed%2C%20involved%20Union%20minister%20Babul%20Supriyo%2C%20(paradoxically%20with%20her%20party%20now)%20for%20serving%20a%20reminder%20during%20a%20verbal%20duel%20on%20TV%2C%20that%20her%20name%20was%20ascribed%20to%20a%20flower%20from%20which%20a%20popular%20indigenous%20alcoholic%20drink%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98arrival%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20Indian%20centre%20stage%20was%20however%2C%20courtesy%20her%202019%20speech.%20Shobha%20De%2C%20the%20high%20priestess%20of%20allusion%20or%20innuendo%2C%20in%20a%20newspaper%20column%2C%20noted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asianage.com%2Fopinion%2Foped%2F290619%2Findia-is-drunk-on-mahua-a-political-star-is-born.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20%E2%80%98birth%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20political%20star%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F683214%2Fparliamentary-ethics-committee-opposition-mps-mahua-moitra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20Slams%20Ethics%20Committee%20Probe%20as%20%E2%80%98Filthy%2C%20Unethical%E2%80%99%2C%20Finds%20Support%20From%20Opposition%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20piece%2C%20more%20space%20was%20devoted%20to%20assertions%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20fielding%20%E2%80%9Castonishingly%20attractive%20female%20candidates%20in%20the%202019%20election%E2%80%9D%20and%20how%20%E2%80%9Caggression%20combined%20with%20sex%20appeal%20works%20best%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20there%20was%20little%20of%20what%20she%20said%2C%20whether%20Moitra%20politically%20stung%20her%20adversaries%20or%20not.%20Effectively%2C%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98form%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20included%20%E2%80%9Ccouture%2C%20or%20handpicked%20stylish%20sarees%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20given%20greater%20importance%20than%20the%20%E2%80%98content%E2%80%99%20of%20her%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20speech%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President%2C%20Moitra%20listed%20seven%20signs%20of%20early%20fascism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India.%20She%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20a%20poster%20on%20fascism%2C%20once%20available%20in%20the%20United%20States%20Holocaust%20Memorial%20Museum.%20It%20included%20%E2%80%9Crampant%20sexism%E2%80%9D%20as%20one%20of%20the%20signs%20of%20onrushing%20fascism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGender-based%20chauvinism%20has%20been%20visible%20in%20abundance%20since%20the%20%E2%80%98case%E2%80%99%20against%20Moitra%20was%20built%20over%20the%20past%20month.%20In%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20meeting%20which%20resulted%20in%20Moitra%20storming%20out%20and%20the%20opposition%20members%20too%20staging%20a%20walk-out%2C%20sexual%20insinuations%20were%20ingrained%20in%20the%20questions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20made%20her%20share%20of%20errors.%20The%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20listed%20to%20pronounce%20her%20guilty%2C%20point%20to%20her%20self-righteousness%20blanking%20the%20ability%20to%20function%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20law.%20Associating%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20with%20her%20political%20campaign%20against%20Modi%20and%20his%20allegedly%20%E2%80%98favourite%E2%80%99%20house%20of%20Adani%2C%20was%20not%20just%20indiscreet%2C%20but%20also%20violated%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20claim%20that%20most%20MPs%20share%20log-in%20IDs%20and%20passwords%20with%20their%20secretarial%20assistants%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20explain%20why%20Hiranandani%20logged%20into%20her%20parliament%20account%20from%20Dubai.%20Further%20criminal%20recommendations%2C%20which%20have%20been%20suggested%2C%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20keep%20Moitra%20preoccupied%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%20She%20would%20possibly%20be%20also%20made%20an%20example%20for%20other%20critics%20and%20prod%20some%20among%20them%20to%20heed%20the%20warnings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cash-for-query%20accusation%20has%20certainly%20not%20been%20proved%20but%20she%20has%20publicly%20accepted%20to%20receiving%20valuable%20gifts%20even%20though%20Moitra%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20purchase%20those%20with%20her%20own%2C%20professionally%20earned%20wealth.%20But%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20often%20not%20so%20rational%20laws%20could%20be%20used%20to%20legally%20haul%20her%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20being%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20most%20Indian%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20run%20on%20democratic%20lines.%20Parties%20are%20mostly%20led%20by%20domineering%20individuals%20and%20the%20TMC%20is%20no%20different.%20Most%20party%20chiefs%20dislike%20strong%20individuals%20with%20ambition%20to%20bolster%20their%20independent%20public%20profile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20erred%20by%20assuming%20that%20her%20efforts%20at%20enhancing%20her%20public%20image%20would%20be%20acceptable%20within%20the%20party%2C%20merely%20because%20she%20was%20taking%20on%20the%20two%20most%20powerful%20intimately%20connected%20individuals.%20The%20nexus%20between%20politics%20and%20business%20%E2%80%93%20across%20parties%20too%2C%20is%20among%20the%20well-known%20realities%20of%20Indian%20polity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20is%20as%20much%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20viciousness%20as%20her%20overzealousness.%20In%20her%20unsparing%20drive%20against%20the%20Modi-Adani%20duo%2C%20Moitra%20erred%20by%20not%20relegating%20to%20the%20backseat%20her%20personal%20efforts%20at%20legitimising%20the%20space%20for%20%E2%80%98her%20kind%E2%80%99%20of%20women%20in%20public%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20fatal%20error%20left%20her%20with%20few%20friends%20outside%20the%20intelligentsia%2C%20inconsequential%20in%20the%20world%20of%20realpolitik.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20has%20been%20made%20of%20the%20hostile%20grilling%20at%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20meeting%20and%20references%20to%20Draupadi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Evastraharan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20disrobing%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20been%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20can%20it%20be%20ignored%20that%20Draupadi%20was%20not%20humiliated%20by%20the%20Kauravas%20alone%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20a%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20epic%20tale%2C%20her%20own%20family%20was%20as%20much%20to%20blame%20for%20her%20being%20shamed%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20before%20the%20%E2%80%98final%E2%80%99%20punishment%20for%20Moitra%20is%20declared%2C%20TMC%20appointed%20her%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Krishnanagar%20district%20unit%20of%20the%20party.%20Is%20this%20evidence%20of%20the%20party%20being%20more%20circumspect%20and%20not%20fully%20backing%20a%20fearless%20parliamentarian%20who%20took%20on%20not%20just%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20powerful%20but%20also%20challenged%20the%20most%20retrograde%20stereotype%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Demolition%20and%20the%20Verdict%3A%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Project%20to%20Reconfigure%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20His%20other%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40NilanjanUdwin.%3