%20Even%20The%20United%20States%20recently%20completed%20the%20transition%20to%20its%20fifth-generation%20Internet2%20at%20400%20gigabits%20per%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Beijing-Wuhan-Guangzhou%20connection%20is%20part%20of%20China's%20Future%20Internet%20Technology%20Infrastructure%2C%C2%A0a%20decade-long%20initiative%20and%20the%20latest%20iteration%20of%20the%20national%20China%20Education%20and%20Research%20Network%20(Cernet).%C2%A0%20Activated%20in%20July%20and%20officially%20launched%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20network%20surpassed%20all%20operational%20tests%20and%20performed%20reliably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20how%20fast%20the%20network%20really%20is%2C%C2%A0Huawei%20Technologies%20vice-president%20Wang%20Lei%20explained%20that%20it%20is%20''capable%20of%20transferring%20the%20data%20equivalent%20of%20150%20high-definition%20films%20in%20just%20one%20second%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20FITI%20project%20leader%20Wu%20Jianping%20from%20the%20Chinese%20Academy%20of%20Engineering%20said%20the%20superfast%20line%20was%20''not%20only%20a%20successful%20operation''%2C%20but%20also%20gives%20China%20the%20''advanced%20technology%20to%20build%20an%20even%20faster%20internet''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXu%20Mingwei%20of%20Tsinghua%20University%2C%20comparing%20the%20new%20internet%20backbone%20to%20a%20superfast%20train%20track%2C%20explained%20that%20it%20replaces%20the%20need%20for%2010%20regular%20tracks%20to%20carry%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20data%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20more%20cost-effective%20and%20manageable%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20system's%20software%20and%20hardware%20has%20been%20domestically%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700036520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fojt40dog_internet-speed_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-launches-worlds-fastest-internet-can