html%5C%22%3EDaily%20Mail%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council's%20(ICC)%20pitch%20consultant%2C%20Andy%20Atkinson%2C%20had%20initially%20stamped%20an%20unused%20surface%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20semi-final%20at%20Wankhede%20but%20the%20decision%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20a%20used%20surface.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20the%20pitch%20which%20would%20be%20in%20play%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20has%20already%20been%20used%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtkinson%20even%20wrote%20an%20e-mail%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20the%20report%20claimed.%20The%20purported%20e-mail%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Daily%20Mail%2C%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20these%20actions%2C%20one%20must%20speculate%20if%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20ever%20(World%20Cup)%20final%20to%20have%20a%20pitch%20which%20has%20been%20specifically%20chosen%20and%20prepared%20to%20their%20stipulation%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20team%20management%20and%2For%20the%20hierarchy%20of%20the%20home%20nation%20board.%20Or%20will%20it%20be%20selected%20or%20prepared%20without%20favouritism%20for%20either%20of%20the%20sides%20competing%20in%20the%20match%20in%20the%20usual%20manner%2C%20and%20unquestionably%20because%20it%20is%20the%20usual%20pitch%20for%20the%20occasion%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20quoted%20a%20BCCI%20official%20as%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20independent%20pitch%20consultant%20works%20with%20the%20host%20and%20venues%20on%20their%20proposed%20pitch%20allocations%2C%20and%20this%20process%20is%20ongoing%20throughout%20an%20event%20of%20this%20length%20and%20nature.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket-world-cup%2Fcricket-world-cup-slow-pitch-expected-for-wankhede-semifinal-on-team-indias-insistence-9026850%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20BCCI%20insisted%20on%20a%20'slow%20pitch'%20for%20the%20semi-final%20against%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGavaskar%2C%20Vaughan%20React%20To%20Pitch%20Change%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20controversy%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20pitch%20is%20there%20for%20all%20the%20teams%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20should%20be%20too%20much%20discussion%20on%20what%20this%20pitch%20will%20do%20or%20not%20do.%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20this%20Indian%20team%20is%20perfectly%20capable%20of%20handling%20any%20kind%20of%20surface.%20Having%20you%20seen%20that%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far.%20And%20if%20it's%20a%20drier%20pitch%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20case%20simply%20because%20the%20rains%20have%20gone.%20So%20there%20will%20be%20there%20is%20no%20hint%20of%20any%20moisture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20will%20be%20one%20which%20there%20might%20be%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20spin%2C%20no%20question%20about%20it.%20But%20the%20Mumbai%20pitch%20is%20generally%20very%20good%20for%20bating%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20should%20be%20too%20much%20of%20an%20issue.%20With%20the%20kind%20of%20bowling%20that%20we%20have%2C%20bowlers%20who%20have%20bowled%20superbly%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20bowling%20first%20or%20second%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20pitch%20would%20be%20too%20much%20of%20an%20issue%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20typically%2C%20you%20know%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%20when%20you%20have%20nothing%20to%20write%20about%20and%20then%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20try%20to%20say%20something%20because%20you%20want%20to%20fill%20in%20your%20columns%2C%20you%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20pitches%20and%20stuff%20like%20that.%20To%20me%2C%20it%20doesn't%20make%20a%20difference.%20If%20the%20pitch%20changes%20after%20the%20toss%2C%20they%20certainly%20have%20a%20conversation.%20But%20if%20the%20pitch%20is%20the%20same%20before%20the%20toss%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20noise%20should%20be%20made%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gavaskar%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Find-vs-nz-sunil-gavaskar-slams-chatter-around-wankhede-pitch-ahead-of-semi-final-clash-2463082-2023-11-15%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20England%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Vaughan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F427-michael-vaughan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Vaughan%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20controversy%2C%20suggesting%20a%20fresh%20pitch%20should%20be%20used%20for%20the%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20World%20Cup%20semi%20should%20be%20played%20on%20a%20fresh%20pitch%20..%20It's%20as%20simple%20as%20that%20..%26quot%3B%20posted%20Vaughan%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20New%20Zealand%20has%20not%20objected%20to%20the%20alleged%20'pitch%20change'%20yet.%20NDTV%20tried%20getting%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20BCCI.%20A%20response%20is%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700035860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fe3p59aag_wankhede-pitch_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwankhede-pitch-swap-controversy-strikes-world-cup-sunil-gavaskar-michael-vaughan-react-4575528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BCCI%2C%20allegedly%2C%20asked%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20Wankhede%20pitch%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20semi-final%20clash%20against%20New%20Zealand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%2