e%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%C2%A0The%20last%20ULB%20and%20panchayat%20elections%20in%20the%20UT%20were%20held%20between%20October%20and%20December%202018%20%E2%80%93%20which%20too%20were%20after%20a%20long%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20made%20the%20official%20disclosure%20on%20Tuesday%20during%20an%20event%20organised%20to%20felicitate%20the%20municipal%20councillors%20who%20had%20completed%20their%20five-year%20tenure%20recently.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20elections%20for%20urban%20local%20bodies%20would%20be%20held%20after%20completion%20of%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20of%20wards%20and%20reservation%20of%20wards%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sinha%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fl-g-jk-civic-polls-will-be-delayed-9027026%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20delay%20would%20mean%20further%20depriving%20J%26amp%3BK%20people%20of%20their%20democratic%20rights%2C%20as%20even%20assembly%20polls%20have%20not%20been%20held%20in%20the%20Union%20territory%20since%202014.%20The%20Union%20government%20and%20local%20administration%20are%20yet%20to%20initiate%20the%20process%20to%20hold%20assembly%20polls%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20delimitation%20process%20of%20assembly%20segments%20had%20concluded%20sometime%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20prompting%20local%20political%20parties%20to%20demand%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20electoral%20activities%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20authorities%20are%20%E2%80%9Cobliged%20to%20prepare%20a%20list%20of%20socially%20and%20educationally%20backward%20classes%20(SEBCs)%2C%20which%20can%20be%20acted%20upon%20for%20providing%20reservation%20to%20OBCs%2C%20including%20in%20election%20to%20local%20governments%E2%80%9D.%20The%20changes%20are%20necessary%20given%20that%20the%20Special%20Status%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20had%20enjoyed%20until%20then%20was%20done%20away%20with%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20orders%2C%20the%20following%20three%20conditions%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20while%C2%A0drawing%20up%20a%20reservation%20plan%3A%20a%20dedicated%20commission%20to%20collect%20empirical%20data%20on%20the%20OBC%20population%2C%20specifying%20the%20proportion%20of%20reservation%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20cumulative%20share%20of%20reserved%20seats%20does%20not%20breach%2050%25%20of%20the%20total%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20G.D.%20Sharma%20Commission%20had%20already%20made%20recommendations%20to%20this%20effect%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%2C%20they%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20accepted%20and%20implemented.%20Even%20after%20the%20administration%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20implement%20OBC%20reservation%2C%20it%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20followed%20up%20with%20the%20identification%20of%20the%20municipal%20constituencies%20to%20be%20reserved%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20time%2C%20the%20official%20pointed%20out.%20There%20are%20more%20administrative%20procedures%20which%20need%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20order%20to%20announce%20and%20hold%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flet-alone-assembly-polls-even-local-body-elections-unlikely-in-jk-before-2024%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20delay%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20local%20unit%20wanting%20to%20defer%20the%20exercise%20at%20least%20till%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20polls.%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20anger%20in%20Dogri-speaking%20areas%20of%20Jammu%20over%20multiple%20governance%20and%20administrative%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20are%20being%20delayed%20despite%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20strengthening%20grassroots%20democracy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20its%20recent%20submission%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20elections%20in%20the%20UT.%20While%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20local%20unit%20is%20publicly%20making%20claims%20about%20being%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20electoral%20battle%2C%20it%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20high%20command%20that%20holding%20local%20body%20elections%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20not%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700034004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15123444%2FThe-Wire-78.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-local-body-polls-wont-be-held-anytime-soon-lg-makes-it-official%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Putting%20an%20end%20to%20speculation%2C%20Manoj%20Sinha%20on%20November%2014%20said%20that%20the%20urban%20local%20body%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20only%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20delimitation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20process%20to%20reserve%20seats%20for%20OBCs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-local-body-polls-wont-be-held-anytime-soon-lg-makes-it-official%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G-DRAGON%20gets%20support%20from%20brother-in-law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700033848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105229350%2Cimgsize-34198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fg-dragon-gets-support-from-brother-in-law-kim-min-joon%2Farticleshow%2F105229402.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cim