0he%20created%20the%20best%20resort%20chain%20in%20India.%20He%20raised%20the%20profile%20of%20the%20Indian%20travel%20and%20hospitality%20sector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EP.R.S.%20Oberoi%20took%20over%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20flagship%20of%20the%20Oberoi%20Group%20nearly%2021%20years%20ago%2C%20in%202002%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%2C%20also%20the%20founding%20chairman%2C%20Mohan%20Singh%20Oberoi.%20He%20was%20CEO%20till%202013%2C%20when%20he%20stepped%20down%20and%20was%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Chairman%20Emeritus%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fp-r-s-oberoi-1929-2023-biki-oberoi-who-set-the-gold-standard-for-hospitality-9026737%2Flite%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Puneet%20Chhatwal%2C%20MD%20and%20CEO%2C%20IHCL%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C(He%20was)%20a%20true%20pioneer%20and%20icon%2C%20he%20leaves%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20impeccable%20hospitality%20that%20will%20be%20cherished%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20transforming%20the%20industry%20landscape%20and%20elevating%20Indian%20hospitality%20on%20a%20global%20stage.%20The%20Oberoi%20Centre%20of%20Learning%20and%20Development%20founded%20by%20him%20has%20groomed%20generations%20of%20fine%20hoteliers%2C%20and%20he%20is%20deeply%20revered%20and%20respected%20by%20the%20many%20lives%20he%20touched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20on%20February%203%2C%201929%2C%20PRS%20Oberoi%20studied%20in%20India%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2Fprs-oberoi-dies-at-94-oberoi-group-chairman-emeritus-indian-hospitality-sector-doyen-2462548-2023-11-14%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20second-highest%20civilian%20honour%2C%20in%20January%202008.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2Fremembering-prithvi-raj-singh-oberoi-aka-biki-oberoi-group-patriarch-dies-at-94.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20writes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20also%20honoured%20with%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Awards%20at%20ILTM%20(International%20Luxury%20Travel%20Market)%20and%20at%206th%20International%20Hotels%20Investment%20Forum%20in%20Berlin.%20He%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Corporate%20Hotelier%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99%20award%20by%20HOTELS%20magazine%20USA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20we%20honour%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mr.%20P.R.S.%20Oberoi%2C%20Chairman%20Emeritus%20of%20The%20Oberoi%20Group.%20His%20passion%20and%20attention%20to%20detail%20shaped%20our%20commitment%20to%20warm%2C%20sincere%2C%20and%20intuitive%20hospitality.%20This%20continued%20quest%20for%20excellence%20will%20drive%20us%20forward.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPRSOberoi%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PRSOberoi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTheOberoiGroup%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TheOberoiGroup%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FII6yJxxCcs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FII6yJxxCcs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Oberoi%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20(%40OberoiHotels)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOberoiHotels%2Fstatus%2F1724434510874616202%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObituaries%20noted%20he%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fprofile%2Fprs-biki-oberoi-indian-hotel-industry-chairman-emeritus-of-oberoi-group-bhuttos-friend-to-design-oberoi-intercontinental-42442%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20termed%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Ca%20stickler%20for%20time%20throughout%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20high%20point%20of%20Biki%20Oberoi%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20the%20hospitality%20industry%20was%20the%20moment%20he%20convinced%20his%20father%2C%20Sardar%20Mohan%20Singh%20Oberoi%20(M.S.%20Oberoi)%2C%20to%20assign%20architect%20and%20politician%20Piloo%20Mody%20to%20design%20Oberoi%20Intercontinental%20in%20the%20capital.%20That%20was%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20and%20many%20acclaimed%20architects%20of%20the%20country%20were%20keen%20to%20grab%20the%20lifetime%20opportunity%20to%20design%20the%20luxury%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20full-page%20newspaper%20advertisements%20marking%20his%20demise%20and%20noting%20his%20career%20as%20a%20pioneer%20in%20luxury%20hospitality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%202008%2C%20as%20armed%20attackers%20terrorised%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20Oberoi%20group%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20hotel%20in%C2%A0Mumbai%C2%A0was%20also%20under%20siege%20and%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20per%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%2C%20note%20that%20he%20used%20to%20narrate%20the%20story%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Gujranwala%20(now%20in%20Pakistan).%20His%20father%2C%20MS%20Oberoi%2C%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Ishran%20Devi%2C%20%E2%80%9Chad%20to%20flee%20their%20native%20village%2C%20Bhaun%2C%20in%20the%20early%201920s%20to%20safeguard%20their%20children%20from%20the%20outbreak%20of%20deadly%20plague.%20They%20moved%20to%20Muree%20(a%20hill%20station%20near%20Rawalpindi)%2C%20where%20M.S.%20Oberoi%20lived%20for%20some%20time%20doing%20odd%20jobs%20before%20moving%20to%20Shimla%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPRS%20Oberoi%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20a%20devout%20and%20proud%20Sikh.%20He%20would%20often%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fprofile%2Fprs-biki-oberoi-indian-hotel-industry-chairman-emeritus-of-oberoi-group-bhuttos-friend-to-design-oberoi-intercontinental-42442%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evisit%20Gurudwara%20Bangla%20Sahib%20for%20prayers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700032180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15123604%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-12.35.0.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fprs-oberoi-biki-passes-away-tributes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20per%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%20emerging%2C%20used%20to%20narrate%20the%20story%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Gujranwala%2C%20now%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fprs-oberoi-biki-passes-away-tributes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Is%20Quietly%20Sending%20Israel%20Ammunition%2C%20Laser-Guided%20Missiles%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20quietly%20ramped%20up%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20delivering%20on%20requests%20that%20include%20more%20laser-guided%20missiles%20for%20its%20Apache%20gunship%20fleet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20155mm%20shells%2C%20night-vision%20devices%2C%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20and%20new%20army%20vehicles%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20Defense%20Department%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapons%20pipeline%20to%20Israel%20is%20extending%20beyond%20the%20well-publicized%20provision%20of%20Iron%20Dome%20interceptors%20and%20Boeing%20Co.%20smart%20bombs.%20It%20continues%20even%20as%20Biden%20administration%20officials%20increasingly%20caution%20Israel%20about%20trying%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20sought%20by%20Israel%20as%20it%20fights%20Hamas%2C%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union%2C%20are%20listed%20in%20a%20document%20labeled%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20Senior%20Leader%26quot%3B%20requests%20that's%20dated%20late%20October%20and%20is%20circulating%20in%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20are%20already%20being%20shipped%20or%20the%20Defense%20Department%20is%20working%20to%20make%20them%20available%20from%20stockpiles%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document%20reviewed%20by%20Bloomberg%20News.%20As%20of%20late%20October%2C%20for%20example%2C%20all%2036%2C000%20rounds%20of%2030mm%20cannon%20ammunition%2C%201%2C800%20of%20the%20requested%20M141%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20and%20at%20least%203%2C500%20night-vision%20devices%20were%20delivered%2C%20the%20tally%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Pentagon%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20discuss%20specifics%2C%20but%20the%20Defense%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bleveraging%20several%20avenues%20-%20from%20internal%20stocks%20to%20U.S.%20industry%20channels%20-%20to%20ensure%20Israel%20has%20the%20means%20to%20defend%20itself.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20security%20assistance%20continues%20to%20arrive%20on%20a%20near-daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%20It%20said%20the%20US%20was%20rapidly%20providing%20precision-guided%20munitions%2C%20small-diameter%20bombs%2C%20155mm%20artillery%20shells%20and%20other%20munitions.%20That's%20along%20with%20Iron%20Dome%20interceptors%20and%20medical%20support%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20of%20artillery%20shells%20and%20other%20munitions%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20nongovernmental%20organizations%20that%20say%20the%20US%20supplies%20have%20allowed%20Israel%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20a%20bombing%20campaign%20that%20Hamas-run%20health%20authorities%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20say%20have%20killed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20Monday%2C%20more%20than%2030%20relief%20organizations%20wrote%20to%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20urging%20him%20not%20to%20send%20the%20155mm%20shells%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Gaza%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%2C%20155mm%20artillery%20shells%20are%20inherently%20indiscriminate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organizations%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20munitions%20are%20unguided%20and%20have%20a%20high%20error%20radius.%26quot%3B%20They%20said%20the%20shells%20often%20land%2025%20meters%20(82%20feet)%20away%20from%20the%20intended%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ammunition%20for%20AH-64%20Apache%20helicopter%20gunships%20includes%20about%202%2C000%20Hellfire%20Laser%20Guided%20missiles%20made%20by%20Lockheed%20Martin%20Corp.%2C%20some%20of%20which%20Israel%20has%20transferred%20to%20its%20forces%20as%20US%20Army%20teams%20seek%20supplies%20from%20stocks%20in%20Germany%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tally.%20It%20also%20includes%20more%20than%2036%2C000%20rounds%20of%2030mm%20ammunition%20to%20be%20fired%20by%20the%20Apache's%20cannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20defense%20forces%20have%20flown%20the%20Boeing-built%20Apaches%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20appears%20to%20be%20using%20the%20Apache%20helicopters%20%26quot%3Bto%20support%20Israel%20troops%20in%20contact%20with%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20using%20their%2030mm%20chain%20guns%20against%20fighters%20caught%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20Hellfire%20missiles%20against%20vehicles%20and%20fighting%20position%20or%20bunkers%20used%20by%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Eisenstadt%2C%20director%20of%20military%20and%20security%20programs%20at%20the%20Washington%20Institute%20for%20Near%20East%20Policy%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20also%20be%20using%20Hellfires%20for%20the%20targeted%20killing%20of%20senior%20commanders%20when%20the%20opportunity%20presents%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReverse%20Trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20requested%20more%20than%2057%2C000%20155mm%20High%20Explosive%20artillery%20shells%20and%2020%2C000%20M4A1%20rifles%2C%20as%20many%20as%205%2C000%20PVS-14%20night%20vision%20devices%2C%203%2C000%20M141%20hand-held%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20that%20US%20Central%20Command%20is%20supplying%2C%20400%20120mm%20mortars%20and%2075%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps'%20new%20Joint%20Light%20Tactical%20Vehicle%2C%20which%20is%20replacing%20the%20Hummer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20tally%2C%20the%20US%20has%20also%20donated%20its%20inventory%20of%20312%20Tamir%20missile%20interceptors.%20The%20Army's%20two%20Iron%20Dome%20batteries%20are%20traveling%20to%20Israel%20by%20sealift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapons%20shipments%20include%20a%20reverse%20trip%20for%20155mm%20shells.%20The%2057%2C000%20had%20been%20sent%20from%20US%20stocks%20in%20Israel%20to%20US%20European%20Command%20locations%20to%20restock%20munitions%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20its%20fight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion.%20Now%20the%20restocked%20munitions%20are%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20Israel%20for%20its%20use%20in%20the%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%2C%20according%20to%20a%20congressional%20aide%20and%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20has%20provided%20more%20than%202%20million%20155mm%20shells%20and%20more%20than%20800%2C000%20105mm%20rounds%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20State%20Department%20summary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitchbla