ests.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20how%20calm%20he%20was%20about%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20hotels%20in%20the%20world%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20burning%20to%20the%20ground.%20After%20the%20call%2C%20he%20continued%20his%20conversation%20with%20me%20and%20another%20colleague%20who%20was%20present%2C%20and%20went%20on%20about%20his%20expectations%20from%20a%20good%20General%20Manager.%20I%20remember%20his%20advice%20that%20day%20-%20focus%20on%20your%20guests%2C%20team%20and%20profitability%2C%20ensure%20that%20you%20cut%20waste%20and%20not%20expenses.%20These%20words%20still%20resonate%20in%20my%20ears.%20The%20phone%20rang%20again%20and%20now%20nearly%20half%20the%20resort%20was%20on%20fire.%20I%20just%20wanted%20the%20meeting%20to%20end%20at%20this%20point%2C%20but%20he%20stayed%20calm%2C%20asking%20us%20specific%20feedback%20on%20the%20new%20resorts%2C%20always%20starting%20with%20-%20what%20can%20we%20do%20better%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20ritual%20of%20fortnightly%20meetings%20with%20Mr.%20Oberoi%2C%20usually%20on%20Sunday%20afternoons%20that%20stretched%20into%20late%20evenings.%20To%20be%20prepared%20for%20them%20one%20had%20to%20start%20a%20day%20in%20advance.%20He%20was%20very%20sharp%2C%20knew%20the%20business%20better%20than%20anyone%20else%20and%20was%20uncompromising%20on%20quality.%20The%20meetings%20would%20be%20around%20operations%20at%20the%20hotels%2C%20new%20initiatives%2C%20revenue%2C%20profitability%2C%20budgets%20and%20hotel%20renovations.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20one%20common%20constant.%20The%20first%20agenda%20before%20the%20start%20of%20these%20meetings%20was%20to%20discuss%20negative%20guest%20reviews%20across%20platforms.%20So%2C%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20hours%20would%20go%20into%20discussing%20guest%20comments%20and%20analysing%20reasons%20behind%20the%20negative%20ones.%20We%20did%20that%20for%2025%20hotels%20even%20before%20meeting%20him%20with%20answers.%20He%20would%20listen%20patiently%20but%20always%20have%20a%20viewpoint%2C%20putting%20the%20guest%20first%2C%20of%20course.%20He%20continued%20this%20practice%20with%20me%20till%20my%20last%20month%20and%20close%20to%20his%2088th%20birthday%2C%20working%20late%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20when%20people%20ask%20me%20how%20we%20create%20a%20culture%20of%20service%20excellence%2C%20I%20just%20tell%20them%2C%20you%20need%20to%20lead%20by%20example%2C%20every%20hour%20and%20everyday.%20All%20the%20time.%20That%20is%20what%20makes%20an%20iconic%20company%20and%20a%20legend.%20And%20that%20is%20who%20he%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kapil%20Chopra%20was%20the%20President%20of%20The%20Oberoi%20Group%20from%202013%20to%202018.%20He%20is%20currently%20the%20Founder%20of%20EazyDiner%20and%20The%20Postcard%20Hotel.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700031180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgqq9cve8_prithviraj-singh_640x480_14_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fresort-on-fire-biki-oberoi-said-protect-team-and-guests-4575218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20would%20listen%20patiently%20but%20always%20have%20a%20viewpoint%2C%20putting%20the%20guest%20first%2C%20of%20course.%20He%20continued%20this%20practice%20with%20me%20till%20my%20last%20month%20and%20close%20to%20his%2088th%20birthday%2C%20working%20late%20into%20the%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fresort-on-fire-biki-oberoi-said-protect-team-and-guests-4575218%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fresort-on-fire-biki-oberoi-said-protect-team-and-guests-4575218%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fresort-on-fire-biki-oberoi-said-protec