tch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20him%2C%20making%20ordinary%20activities%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20Fall%20From%20Grace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115004%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-11.49.15-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incomparable%20James%20Baldwin%20pronounced%20with%20profound%20simplicity%20that%20%E2%80%9Cone%20writes%20out%20of%20one%20thing%20only%20%E2%80%93%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20from%20that%20experience%20tries%20to%20wrench%20out%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20last%20drop%2C%20sweet%20or%20bitter%20it%20can%20give.%E2%80%9D%20How%20true%20of%20the%20writer%E2%80%99s%20craft%2C%20even%20that%20of%20a%20lowly%20hack!%20This%20composition%20is%2C%20after%20a%20fashion%2C%20the%20upshot%20of%20an%20association%20of%20ideas%2C%20events%20and%20people%20relating%20to%20the%20experience%20of%20corruption.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20a%20story%20of%20a%20nemesis%20confronting%20hubris!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20recent%20essay%20on%20the%20monstrous%20corruption%20under%20the%20present%20regime%20provoked%20remonstrations%20from%20some%20critics%20who%20chastised%20me%20for%20describing%20the%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20(IAC)%20movement%20steered%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20%E2%80%98messianic%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20force%20for%20good%2C%20for%20ramming%20through%20the%20groundbreaking%20Lokpal%20Act%20in%202013.%20I%20was%20admonished%20for%20bestowing%20a%20halo%20on%20what%20was%20a%20sanctimonious%20and%20disingenuous%20middle-class%20uprising%20against%20political%20corruption%20that%2C%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20infamous%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20Vinod%20Rai%20and%20his%20trumped-up%20national%20loss%20of%20Rs%201.76%20lakh%20crores%20to%20the%20Exchequer%20apropos%20of%20the%202G%20spectrum%20allotment%2C%20cleared%20the%20way%20for%20the%20alleged%20but%20now%20absolved%20conductor%20of%20Gujarat%202002.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20critics%E2%80%99%20view%2C%20it%20was%20ultimately%20not%20about%20fighting%20corruption%20but%20a%20deep-rooted%20RSS-backed%20plot%20to%20wrest%20control%20of%20the%20polity.%20One%20should%20have%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20smell%20the%20rat%20when%20Kejriwal%20roped%20in%20Hindutva%20icons%20Ramdev%20and%20Sri%20Sri%20Ravishankar%20to%20the%20IAC%20fold.%20Much%20later%2C%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20one%20of%20IAC%E2%80%99s%20leading%20lights%2C%20conceded%20that%20his%20outfit%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpropped%20up%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20almost%20all%20my%20critics%20were%20at%20one%20time%20passionate%20devotees%20of%20Kejriwal%20and%20gang.%20Who%20wasn%E2%80%99t%3F%20The%20entire%20country%20was%20initially%20suckered%20into%20believing%20the%20third-rate%20cops-and-robbers%20narrative%20spun%20by%20these%20self-righteous%20do-gooders.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20cabal%20%E2%80%93%20with%20Anna%20Hazare%20as%20bewildered%20talisman%20%E2%80%93%20were%20perceived%20as%20starry-eyed%20idealists%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20awaken%20people%20to%20the%20rot%20in%20the%20system.%20Despite%20a%20host%20of%20seasoned%20professionals%20and%20intellectuals%20in%20the%20IAC%2C%20it%20was%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20upstart%20who%20usurped%20the%20leadership%20mantle%20through%20sheer%20ingenious%20guile.%20To%20give%20the%20devil%20credit%2C%20he%20was%20undoubtedly%20the%20moving%20force%20in%20the%20crusade%20against%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20was%20unknown%20at%20that%20time%20was%20his%20absolute%20craving%20for%20power.%20And%20his%20unbridled%20ambition%20was%20far%20from%20quenched%20by%20bringing%20the%20venal%20UPA%20government%20to%20its%20knees%20and%20forcing%20through%20the%20Lokpal%20Act.%20Having%20got%20a%20taste%20of%20power%2C%20albeit%20without%20accountability%2C%20he%20lusted%20for%20more.%20Kejriwal%20realised%20that%20the%20anti-corruption%20movement%20had%20run%20its%20course%20and%20he%20needed%20to%20migrate%20to%20where%20the%20real%20power%20was%20to%20remain%20relevant%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20late%202012%2C%20Kejriwal%20broke%20away%20from%20Anna%20Hazare%20who%20had%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20expended%20his%20usefulness%20as%20titular%20head%20of%20the%20anti-corruption%20campaign.%20But%20the%20rumoured%20trigger%20for%20the%20parting%20of%20ways%20was%20the%20issue%20of%20converting%20the%20IAC%20movement%20into%20a%20political%20entity.%20Even%20as%20the%20old%20man%20faded%20into%20insignificance%2C%20Kejriwal%20formed%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20determined%20to%20exploit%20the%20mass%20public%20support%20and%20goodwill%20generated%20by%20the%20IAC%20movement.%20His%20instincts%20were%20spot%20on%20as%20the%20new%20kids%20on%20the%20block%20emerged%20ahead%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20with%2028%20of%20the%2070%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20the%202013%20Delhi%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farivnd-kejriwal-poker-deities-cards-currency-note%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20Latest%20Gambit%20is%20Politics%20as%20Deadly%20Poker%20With%20Deities%20as%20Cards%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202015%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20this%20fledgling%20party%20won%20a%20resounding%20victory%2C%20claiming%2067%20of%20the%2070%20seats%2C%20decimating%20the%20two%20major%20political%20parties.%20AAP%20struck%20a%20chord%20among%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20masses%20with%20its%20message%20of%20a%20moral%20political%20order%20based%20on%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20people%20and%20devolution%20of%20powers%20to%20the%20grassroots.%20It%20denounced%20caste%20and%20community-based%20politics%20and%20upheld%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20individual%20and%20her%20right%20to%20essential%20goods%20including%20free%20water%20and%20subsidised%20electricity.%20It%20purveyed%20an%20ideological%20neutrality%20that%20sought%20to%20absorb%20the%20best%20in%20capitalism%20and%20socialism.%20A%20party%20comprising%20academics%2C%20lawyers%2C%20technocrats%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20actors%2C%20holy%20men%2C%20et%20al%20spoke%20an%20audacious%20democratic%20idiom%20that%20held%20out%20hope%20of%20a%20brave%20new%20form%20of%20governance%20free%20of%20corruption%20and%20based%20on%20the%20well-being%20and%20collective%20will%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20it%20has%20turned%20out%2C%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20based%20on%20a%20big%20lie!%20The%20Bible%20proclaims%20that%20God%20created%20man%20in%20his%20own%20image.%20Likewise%2C%20a%20powerful%20leader%20inevitably%20moulds%20his%20party%20into%20a%20mirror%20reflection%20of%20his%20personality%20and%20character.%20And%20when%20the%20leader%20is%20self-obsessive%2C%20the%20party%20is%20subsumed%20under%20the%20sheer%20weight%20of%20his%20egomaniacal%20persona.%20Both%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20been%20morally%20crippled%20by%20such%20supermen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20striking%20similarities%20between%20Kejriwal%20and%20the%20Vishwaguru.%20Although%20the%20bush%20shirted%20and%20mufflered%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20aadm%3C%2Fem%3Ei%20(common%20man)%20is%20sartorially%20very%20different%20from%20the%20dandy%20accoutred%20in%20Maybach%20shades%20and%20flashy%20kurtas%2C%20they%20share%20much%20in%20common.%20They%20are%20machiavellian%20realists%20possessed%20of%20an%20all-consuming%20lust%20for%20power%2C%20who%20refuse%20to%20be%20distracted%20by%20considerations%20of%20right%20and%20wrong.%20They%20traffic%20in%20falsehoods%20and%20are%20so%20addicted%20to%20lying%20that%20exaggeration%20is%20their%20nearest%20link%20to%20the%20truth.%20They%20shamelessly%20parade%20religion%20in%20the%20public%20square%20for%20personal%20benefit%2C%20heedless%20of%20the%20damage%20it%20does%20to%20the%20secular%20fabric.%20They%20take%20credit%20when%20things%20are%20going%20well%20but%20are%20deft%20at%20deflecting%20blame%20when%20anything%20bombs.%20The%20universe%20is%20only%20about%20them!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVery%20early%20in%20the%20piece%2C%20Kejriwal%20decided%20to%20hitch%20his%20lot%20to%20self-serving%20power%20politics.%20Autocratic%20to%20the%20core%2C%20he%20went%20about%20neutralising%20anyone%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20competitor%20or%20pricked%20his%20conscience.%20Much%20like%20the%20Vishwaguru%20who%2C%20without%20ado%2C%20consigned%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20veteran%20leaders%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20M.M.%20Joshi%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emargdarshak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eback%20burner%2C%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20first%20significant%20move%20was%20to%20banish%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20and%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20who%20represented%20the%20conscience%20of%20AAP%20and%20incessantly%20reminded%20him%20of%20the%20moral%20code%20that%20was%20the%20raison%20d%E2%80%99etre%20of%20the%20party.%20In%20another%20cynical%20move%2C%20he%20nominated%20two%20nonentities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20businessman%20and%20a%20CA%20belonging%20to%20his%20caste%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20ignoring%20luminaries%20who%20had%20slaved%20for%20the%20party%2C%20provoking%20allegations%20that%20he%20had%20traded%20the%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20clearest%20pointer%20to%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20metamorphosis%20into%20an%20amoral%2C%20power-hungry%20politician%20has%20been%20his%20stance%20on%20the%20Lokpal%20as%20head%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government.%20The%20Jan%20Lokpal%20Bill%20passed%20in%202015%20by%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20has%20still%20not%20been%20ratified%20into%20law%20%E2%80%93%20the%20casualty%20in%20an%20unending%20saga%20of%20obfuscation%20and%20bitter%20recrimination%20between%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20neither%20keen%20on%20an%20independent%20ombudsman.%20Another%20indicator%20of%20his%20transformation%20into%20a%20hardened%2C%20reprobate%20leader%20was%20his%20abortive%20attempt%20to%20wrest%20control%20of%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20of%20the%20state%20in%20direct%20contravention%20of%20the%20IAC%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20credo%20that%20anti-corruption%20units%20should%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20political%20executive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-lakshmi-ganesh-hindu-currency-modi%5C%22%3E%20Neither%20%E2%80%98Pro-Hindu%E2%80%99%20nor%20%E2%80%98Anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%2C%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20Monetary%20Genius%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Mould%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20man%E2%80%99s%20real%20character%20is%20revealed%20in%20dire%20adversity.%20Long%20ago%2C%20Dante%20said%20that%20the%20hottest%20places%20in%20hell%20are%20reserved%20for%20those%20who%20are%20non-aligned%20in%20times%20of%20grave%20crisis.%20The%20riots%20in%20North-East%20Delhi%20in%202020%20called%20Kejriwal%20out%20for%20the%20diabolically%20amoral%20politician%20that%20he%20is.%20The%20mayhem%20over%20four%20nightmarish%20days%20was%20an%20awful%20exhibition%20of%20human%20depravity%2C%20perhaps%20the%20worst%20since%20the%20Sikh%20pogrom%20in%201984.%20At%20this%20critical%20time%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20went%20missing%2C%20using%20the%20fig%20leaf%20that%20law%20and%20order%20was%20not%20his%20domain.%20A%20man%20who%20has%20sought%20the%20limelight%20in%20every%20situation%2C%20played%20the%20artful%20dodger%20when%20his%20people%20needed%20him%20most%20for%20the%20treacherous%20reason%20that%20any%20intervention%20would%20antagonise%20the%20majority%20community%3B%20so%20he%20let%20people%20die.%20English%20revolutionary%20Thomas%20Paine%20had%20people%20like%20Kejriwal%20in%20mind%20when%20he%20observed%20that%20the%20cunning%20of%20the%20fox%20is%20as%20murderous%20as%20the%20violence%20of%20the%20wolf.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20memorable%20quotation%20credited%20to%20Kejriwal%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CPower%20does%20not%20corrupt%20men%3B%20fools%20(and%20I%20would%20add%20%E2%80%9Cknaves%E2%80%9D)%2C%20however%2C%20if%20they%20get%20into%20a%20position%20of%20power%2C%20corrupt%20power.%E2%80%9D%20The%20author%20of%20the%20phrase%20is%2C%20in%20truth%2C%20Irish%20playwright%20George%20Bernard%20Shaw.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20Shaw%20quote%20that%20he%20usurped%20fits%20him%20like%20a%20glove.%20Having%20betrayed%20the%20enormous%20faith%20and%20goodwill%20of%20his%20people%2C%20the%20hubristic%20preacher%20on%20public%20morality%20is%20today%20running%20scared%2C%20fearful%20of%20being%20sent%20to%20jail%20for%20alleged%20corruption.%20Is%20it%20%3Cem%3Ek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Earma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20catching%20up%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20in%20the%20next%20election%2C%20confronted%20with%20a%20Hobson%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20deciding%20between%20the%20devil%20and%20a%20bigger%20devil%2C%20the%20elector%20might%20still%20opt%20for%20the%20devil.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20far%20gone%20we%20are%20in%20the%20all-pervasive%20venality%20of%20our%20politics!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700030330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115004%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-11.49.15-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwals-fall-from-grace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Autocratic%20to%20the%20core%2C%20Kejriwal%20went%20about%20neutralising%20anyone%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20competitor%20or%20pricked%20his%20conscience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwals-fall-from-grace%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Boy%20Killed%20In%20Monkey%20Attack%2C%20Officials%20Say%20Intestines%20Ripped%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2010-year-old%20boy%20was%20brutally%20killed%20by%20a%20monkey%20after%20it%20ripped%20into%20his%20stomach%20and%20tore%20out%20his%20intestines.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Salki%20village%20in%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20forest%20officials%20added%20that%20the%20monkey%20attack%20happened%20near%20a%20temple%20in%20Dehgam%20Taluka.%20The%20police%20identified%20the%20victim%20as%20Dipak%20Thakor.%20The%20boy%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%20but%20tragically%20died%20before%20doctors%20could%20even%20begin%20to%20help%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20and%20forest%20officials%20said%20that%20Dipak%20was%20playing%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20small%20village%20when%20he%20was%20terrorised%20by%20a%20notorious%20gang%20of%20monkeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apes%20then%20jumped%20onto%20the%20boy%20and%20punctured%20his%20skin%20before%20digging%20their%20claws%20inside%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20intestine%20was%20ripped%20out%20in%20the%20attack.%20He%20rushed%20to%20his%20house%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20where%20doctors%20declared%20him%20dead%20on%20arrival%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20third%20attack%20by%20monkeys%20in%20the%20village%20within%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForest%20official%20Vishal%20Chaudhary%20said%20the%20department%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20catch%20the%20monkeys%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20rescued%20two%20langurs%20in%20the%20past%20one%20week%2C%20and%20set%20up%20cages%20to%20trap%20another%20langur.%20There%20is%20a%20large%20troop%20of%20monkeys%20in%20the%20village%2C%20including%20four%20adults%20who%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20attacks%20in%20the%20past%20one%20week.%20Two%20of%20them%20have%20been%20rescued.%20Efforts%20are%20on%20to%20cage%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vishal%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20monkey%20with%20a%20Rs%2021%2C000%20bounty%20on%20its%20head%20was%20caught%20after%20terrorising%20people%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Rajgarh%20town%20for%20two%20weeks%20during%20which%20it%20attacked%2020%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescue%20team%20used%20a%20drone%20to%20locate%20the%20monkey%2C%20managed%20to%20tranquilise%20it%20using%20darts%20and%20then%20put%20it%20in%20a%20cage.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700030280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Ftojc19ig_monkey-generic-unsplash_625x300_13_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-boy-killed-in-monkey-attack-officials-say-intestines-ripped-out-4575346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20and%20forest%20officials%20said%20that%20Dipak%20was%20playing%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20small%20village%20when%20he%20was%20terrorised%20by%20a%20notorious%20gang%20of%20monkeys.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-boy-killed-in-monkey-attack-officials-say-intestines-ripped-out-4575346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-boy-killed-in-monkey-attack-officials-say-intestines-ripped-out-4575346%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-boy-killed-in-monkey-attack-officials-say-intestines-ripped-out-4575346%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Copy%20Paste'%2C%20'Hindi%20Imposition'%3A%20What%20Opposition%20MPs'%20Dissent%20Notes%20on%20the%20Criminal%20Bills%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115956%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Eight%20opposition%20MPs%20have%20given%20dissent%20notes%20to%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs%20that%20was%20tasked%20to%20examine%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-three-criminal-law-bills-using-criminal-law-to-establish-permanent-extra-constitutional-emergency-powers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20new%20criminal%20bills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MPs%20have%20called%20the%20new%20legislations%20%E2%80%9Clargely%20a%20copy%20paste%E2%80%9D%20of%20existing%20laws%2C%20opposed%20their%20Hindi%20names%2C%20flagged%20lack%20of%20consultation%20and%20diversity%20of%20domain%20expert%20opinion%20and%20questioned%20the%20%E2%80%9Chaste%E2%80%9D%20in%20which%20the%20legislations%20are%20being%20introduced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20new%20bills%20including%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%20to%20replace%20the%C2%A0%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20Bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%2C%201973%20%E2%80%93%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20parliament%20on%20August%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bills%20were%20then%20referred%20to%20the%2031-member%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-adopts-reports-on-three-criminal-bills-several-dissent-notes-from-opposition%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadopted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20report%20last%20week.%20The%20committee%20was%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Lal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20MPs%20who%20gave%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FSC_Report_Bharatiya_Sakshya_Bill_2023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edissent%20notes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20include%20Congress%20MP%20and%20former%20home%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20his%20party%20colleagues%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Ravneet%20Singh%20and%20Digvijaya%20Singh%3B%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20N.R.%20Elango%20and%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%20and%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20and%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Largely%20a%20copy%20and%20paste%20of%20existing%20laws%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20dissent%20note%20to%20the%20three%20bills%2C%20Chidambaram%20said%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Clargely%20a%20copy%20and%20paste%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20existing%20laws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20absolutely%20no%20need%20to%20draft%20so-called%20new%20Bills.%20All%20that%20the%20Bills%20have%20done%20is%20to%20make%20a%20few%20amendments%20(some%20acceptable%2C%20some%20not%20acceptable)%2C%20re-arrange%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20existing%20Laws%2C%20and%20merge%20different%20sections%20into%20one%20section%20with%20many%20sub-sections.%20This%20is%20a%20wasteful%20exercise%20that%20will%20have%20many%20undesirable%20consequences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20dissent%20notes%2C%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20and%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20the%20new%20bills%20are%20%E2%80%9C93%25%20copy%20paste%20legislation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EO%E2%80%99Brien%20wrote%20that%20the%20pre-existing%20legislation%20could%20have%20been%20modified%20to%20incorporate%20specific%20changes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MPs%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20Chowdhury%20and%20Ravneet%20Singh%20wrote%20that%20the%20laws%20are%20vastly%20the%20same%20and%20have%20only%20been%20renumbered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exercise%2C%20experts%20opine%2C%20would%20be%20responsible%20for%20large%20scale%20confusion%20resulting%20in%20unnecessary%20delay%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20courts%20and%20the%20policing%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Digvijiya%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20note%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20MPs%20added%20that%20even%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20parliament%20while%20introducing%20the%20bills%2C%20the%20changes%20amount%20to%2025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20thus%20no%20need%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20unnecessary%20reform%20for%20merely%2012%20substantive%20amendments%20(by%20the%20HM%E2%80%99s%20own%20examples).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Hindi%20imposition%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20dissenting%20notes%20almost%20all%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20have%20written%20against%20the%20Hindi%20names%20of%20the%20bills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChidambaram%20cited%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20constitution%20that%20states%20that%20all%20Acts%20shall%20be%20in%20the%20English%20language%20which%20is%20also%20the%20language%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20High%20Courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20have%20a%20Hindi%20only%20name%20to%20the%20Bill%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20language%20of%20the%20Bill%20is%20highly%20objectionable%2C%20unconstitutional%2C%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20people%20(e.g.%20Tamils%2C%20Gujaratis%20or%20Bengalis)%20and%20opposed%20to%20federalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDMK%20MP%20Maran%20said%20that%20the%20bills%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20further%20change%20the%20federal%20relationship%20and%20structure%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20the%20State.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20bills%20tum%20into%20Act%E2%80%99s%2C%20the%20people%20in%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20states%20will%20find%20difficulty%20in%20pronouncing%20and%20handling%20these%20Acts.%20At%20the%20grass%20root%20level%20they%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20texture%2C%20character%2C%20tenor%2C%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20act%20if%20the%20title%20remains%20in%20Hindi%20and%20implementation%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20including%20filing%20of%20FIR%E2%80%99s.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDMK%20MP%20Elango%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20not%20considered%20the%20suggestions%20on%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20bills%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%20which%20undermines%20federalism%20in%20as%20much%20as%20it%20%E2%80%9Cgoes%20against%20the%20linguistic%20feelings%20of%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20Indians.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20said%20that%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20bills%20in%20Hindi%2C%20amounts%20to%20not%20only%20%E2%80%9CHindi%20imposition%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Lack%20of%20consultation%2C%20diversity%20of%20opinion%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20in%20their%20dissent%20notes%20have%20also%20flagged%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20consultation%20in%20drafting%20the%20bills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChidambaram%20said%20that%20besides%20state%20governments%2C%20Bar%20Associations%2C%20State%20and%20Central%20Police%20organisations%2C%20the%20Indian%20Police%20Foundation%2C%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20Universities%2C%20judges%20of%20the%20subordinate%20judiciary%20who%20apply%20the%20laws%20every%20day%2C%20eminent%20retired%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20High%20Courts%2C%20eminent%20senior%20advocates%20and%20legal%20scholars%20were%20not%20consulted%20at%20the%20consideration%20stage%20by%20circulating%20the%20draft%20Bills%20and%20inviting%20them%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20object%20to%20the%20process%20followed%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20insufficiency%2C%20non-%20inclusionary%2C%20non%20scholarly%20and%20lack%20of%20adequate%20time%20for%20consideration%20by%20the%20Members%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EO%E2%80%99Brien%20also%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20procedure%20lacked%20inclusivity%20in%20stakeholder%20consultations.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20the%20people%20called%20to%20testify%20had%20strong%20leanings%20or%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20note%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20letters%20that%20he%20had%20sent%20to%20the%20chairperson%20(attached%20in%20his%20dissent%20note)%20and%20said%20that%20multiple%20verbal%20and%20written%20requests%20had%20been%20made%20by%20the%20undersigned%20to%20invite%20experts%20and%20practitioners%20to%20testify.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDrafting%20errors%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20also%20pointed%20to%20what%20they%20called%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdrafting%20errors%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20legislations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20dissent%20note%20Chidambaram%20said%20that%20he%20had%20pointed%20to%20drafting%20errors%20but%20only%20some%20have%20been%20adopted%20and%20added%20that%20both%20%E2%80%9Cimprisonment%20for%20life%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cimprisonment%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20natural%20life%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20separately%20defined%20and%20used%20in%20appropriate%20sections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20a%20definition%20should%20also%20be%20provided%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccommunity%20service%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFlagging%20such%20errors%20in%20the%20bills%20and%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstunt%20before%202024%20elections%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Chasty%20passage%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20bills%20may%20result%20in%20%E2%80%9Cunintended%20consequences%20and%20contribute%20to%20public%20dissatisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EO%E2%80%99Brien%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20committee%20had%20limited%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20meaningful%20participation%20of%20the%20opposition%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20meetings%20were%20scheduled%20during%20the%20festive%20season%20when%20members%20had%20prior%20constituency%20engagements%20and%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20was%20allowed%20only%20an%20hour%20to%20scrutinise%20and%20critique%20the%20bills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Essentially%20colonial%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20MPs%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20Chowdhury%20and%20Ravneet%20Singh%20in%20their%20dissent%20notes%20said%20that%20the%20laws%20were%20%E2%80%9Cessentially%20colonial%E2%80%9D%20even%20though%20the%20stated%20purpose%20of%20the%20exercise%20was%20to%20shed%20the%20colonial%20nature%20of%20the%20criminal%20laws.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20most%20punishments%20for%20offences%20under%20the%20IPC%20have%20been%20retained.%20Further%2C%20punishments%20for%20some%20offences%20have%20been%20made%20harsher%20and%20the%20death%20penalty%20has%20been%20added%20for%20at%20least%20four%20new%20crimes%20such%20as%20mob%20lynching%2C%20organised%20crime%2C%20terrorism%20and%20rape%20of%20a%20minor.%20The%20removal%20of%20law%20on%20sedition%20was%20a%20mere%20symbolic%20gesture%20as%20it%20is%20replaced%20by%20a%20Clause%20150%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Samhita%20which%20is%20much%20more%20tyrannical%20and%20colonial%20in%20its%20essence.%20Ultimately%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20shift%20towards%20a%20rehabilitative%20approach%20to%20criminal%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20notes%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20MPs%20have%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20use%20of%20handcuffs%C2%A0%20under%20clause%2043(3)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%20which%20allows%20the%20use%20of%20handcuffs%20by%20police%20officers%20for%20certain%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%C2%A0%20in%201980%20which%20held%20that%20handcuffs%20are%20an%20anathema%20to%20human%20dignity%2C%20the%20Congress%20MPs%20stated%20that%20this%20section%20is%20more%20in%20line%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccolonial%20mindset%20of%20punitive%20control%20of%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Enhances%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policing%20powers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20also%20said%20that%20the%20bills%20enhance%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20policing%20powers%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20any%20checks%20and%20balances.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20enhance%20the%20time%20for%20which%20a%20person%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20there%20exists%20no%20protective%20measures%20to%20provide%20safety%20to%20the%20accused%20persons%20under%20police%20custody%20which%20is%20bound%20to%20adversely%20affect%20the%20safety%20of%20detainees%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20in%20his%20note.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20MPs%20added%20that%20by%20increasing%20the%20period%20of%20detention%20beyond%20the%20period%20of%20fifteen%20days%2C%20the%20new%20laws%20have%20ignored%20and%20undone%20the%20safeguard%20of%20judicial%20custody%20where%20police%20have%20to%20take%20Magistrate%E2%80%99s%20permission%20to%20interrogate%20an%20accused.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20TMC%20MPs%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20and%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20increasing%20the%20period%20of%20police%20custody%20without%20proper%20safeguards%20could%20lead%20to%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20%E2%80%9Cincluding%20the%20risk%20of%20torture%2C%20coerced%20confessions%2C%20and%20abuse%20of%20detainees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20particularly%20concerning%20given%20the%20history%20of%20custodial%20violence%20and%20abuse%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Ghosh%20Dastidar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Abolish%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Ed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cb%3Eeath%20penalty%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20have%20also%20written%20against%20the%20retention%20of%20the%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20consider%2C%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%20death%20penalty.%20Humanism%20will%20ever%20be%20grateful%20to%20us%20if%20we%20deliberate%20and%20abolish%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Elango.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20National%20Law%20University%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20justice%20programme%20Project%2039A%2C%20both%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20and%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20re-evaluate%20death%20penalty%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGhosh%20Dastidar%E2%80%99s%20note%20said%20that%20a%20significant%20majority%20of%20death%20row%20inmates%20come%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%2C%20lacking%20proper%20education%2C%20and%20belonging%20to%20marginalised%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20data%20underscores%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20re-evaluating%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChidambaram%20in%20his%20note%20stated%20that%20it%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cestablished%20that%20death%20penalty%20is%20no%20deterrent%20to%20serious%20crimes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20natural%20life%20without%20parole%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20more%20rigorous%20punishment%20and%20also%20opens%20a%20window%20of%20opportunity%20for%20the%20convict%20to%20reform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESedition%20law%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20dissent%20note%2C%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20the%20sedition%20law%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cretained%20with%20a%20broader%20definition%20that%20can%20encompass%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20actions%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20endangering%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity%20and%20integrity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20expansion%20of%20the%20law%20provides%20authorities%20with%20significant%20discretion%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%2C%20which%20called%20for%20a%20well-defined%20sedition%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20note%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EO%E2%80%99Brien%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%20does%20not%20explicitly%20have%20a%20Section%20124A%20(IPC%20section%20that%20refers%20to%20sedition)%20it%20has%20Section%20150%2C%20which%20reintroduces%20sedition%20in%20the%20bills%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20draconian%20manner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMarital%20rape%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20MPs%20also%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20stated%20purpose%20of%20the%20legislations%20being%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20marital%20rape%20has%20not%20been%20criminalised%20in%20the%20bills.%20They%20also%20objected%20to%20Clause%2069%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Samhita%20that%20refers%20to%20sexual%20intercourse%20by%20employing%20deceitful%20means%20and%20stated%20that%20deceitful%20means%20is%20too%20broad%20and%20can%20be%20prone%20to%20misuse%20to%20harass%20interfaith%20and%20inter%20caste%20couples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700029961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115956%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcriminal-bills-opposition-mp-dissent-note-hindi-imposition-copy-paste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20opposition%20MPs%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20TMC%2C%20and%20DMK%20have%20submitted%20dissent%20notes%20to%20the%20report%20adopted%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20home%20affairs%20and%20flagged%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20Bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcriminal-bills-opposition-mp-dissent-note-hindi-imposition-copy-paste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20weightage%20climbs%20to%20highest%20level%20on%20MSCI%20Global%20Standard%20index%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700029395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-06%2F21%2Ffull%2F1498062358-153.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findia-s-wei