%20Moreh%20and%20sending%20them%20across%20towards%20Tamu%20(nearest%20Myanmar%20town%20from%20Moreh)%20was%20over%20by%203%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Army%20officer%20monitoring%20the%20exercise%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F39-myanmar-soldiers-who-entered-mizoram-sent-back%2Farticle67532430.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20also%20added%20that%20there%20were%20reports%20of%20two%20more%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20crossing%20over%20into%20India%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%20He%20said%20they%20would%20also%20be%20sent%20back%20once%20security%20personnel%20locates%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20since%20February%202021%2C%20intensified%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20in%20the%20region%20close%20to%20the%20Mizoram%20border.%20The%20fighting%20between%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Army%20and%20pro-democracy%20groups%2C%20including%20ethnicity-based%20extremist%20groups%2C%20has%20gone%20up%20by%20several%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Indian%20security%20officials%2C%20a%20fierce%20gunfight%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20two%20sides%C2%A0at%20Khawmawi%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20is%20located%20across%20Zokhawthar%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Champhai%20district%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2012%20evening.%20About%201%2C500%20Myanmarese%20have%20been%20taking%20refuge%20in%20border%20areas%20of%20Mizoram%20following%20the%20gunfight%2C%20officials%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%20aligned%20with%20the%20pro-democracy%20movement%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20Kuki%20Independent%20Army%2C%20Kuki%20National%20Army%2C%20and%20the%20Chinland%20Defence%20Force%20also%20attacked%20the%20Myanmarese%20military%20camp%20in%20Mizoram.%20A%20military%20camp%20in%20Rikhawdar%20near%20Khawmawi%20was%20also%20overrun%20by%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%