-crisis-1-month-cases-surge-apex-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20hard%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20living%20there%20at%20the%20start%20of%202020%20was%20a%20scary%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20was%20like%20a%20ghost%20town%20filled%20with%20the%20noise%20of%20ambulance%20sirens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20in%20Taiwan%20in%20September%202020%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20prisoner%20for%20the%20two%20weeks%20I%20was%20in%20quarantine%2C%20but%20life%20after%20that%20was%20basically%20back%20to%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20real%20jolt%20coming%20straight%20from%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20just%20the%20way%20Taipei%20handled%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it's%20how%20much%20more%20safe%2C%20functional%2C%20and%20clean%20the%20city%20feels%20in%20comparison%20to%20NYC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20New%20Yorker%20knows%20there%20are%20many%20places%20in%20the%20city%20where%20you'd%20feel%20vulnerable%20walking%20through%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20safe%20walking%20down%20any%20street%20at%20any%20time%20of%20day%20in%20Taipei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20Google%20Maps%20told%20me%20it'd%20take%2030%20minutes%20to%20get%20somewhere%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I'd%20allocate%20an%20hour%20because%20of%20how%20unreliable%20the%20subway%20is.%20In%20Taipei%2C%20the%20same%20estimate%20often%20means%20arriving%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20only%20started%20learning%20Mandarin%20after%20accepting%20the%20job%20offer%2C%20I've%20found%20it%20really%20easy%20to%20assimilate%2C%20as%20people%20are%20extremely%20friendly%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20figuring%20out%20a%20way%20to%20continue%20to%20stay%20here%20after%20my%20postdoctoral%20position%20ends%20has%20become%20my%20top%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I%20don't%20need%20more%20than%20%2440%2C000%20a%20year%20to%20thrive%20in%20Taipei%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Dingxi%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20Yonghe%20district%20of%20Taipei%2C%20where%20Alex%20Teachey%20lives.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553102736d588dc55cfb9f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dingxi%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20Yonghe%20district%20of%20Taipei%2C%20where%20Alex%20Teachey%20lives.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Teachey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20received%20the%20job%20offer%20to%20come%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20I%20thought%3A%20Wow%2C%20this%20salary%20is%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20low.%20But%20after%20living%20here%20for%20three%20years%2C%20I%20can%20safely%20say%20it's%20enough%20to%20live%20comfortably%20on%20in%20Taipei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20by%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20fourth-floor%20walk-up%20built%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20a%20typical%20Taiwanese%20family%20home.%20I%20pay%20around%20%24800%20in%20rent%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20in%20a%20neighborhood%20that%20I%20love%2C%20in%20New%20Taipei%20City%2C%20the%20enormous%20donut%20that%20sprawls%20around%20the%20center%20of%20Taipei.%20I%20live%20a%2020-minute%20bike%20ride%20from%20my%20office%20%E2%80%94%20I%20never%20could%20have%20have%20afforded%20anything%20remotely%20similar%20if%20I'd%20stayed%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20rent%2C%20the%20other%20big%20chunk%20of%20my%20expenses%20comes%20from%20food.%20My%20sense%20of%20what%20counts%20as%20an%20expensive%20meal%20has%20changed%20a%20lot%3A%20Here%2C%20my%20lunches%20cost%20between%20100%20to%20200%20Taiwan%20dollars%2C%20or%20between%20%243%20to%20%246.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20spent%20500%20Taiwan%20dollars%20on%20a%20meal%2C%20I'd%20feel%20like%3A%20Wow%2C%20it's%20my%20birthday.%20And%20that's%20less%20than%20what%20I%20would%20spend%20on%20a%20Chipotle%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20issue%20that%20I've%20faced%20though%2C%20is%20that%20when%20you%20travel%20out%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20you%20really%20do%20feel%20how%20low%20your%20wages%20are%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20number%20one%20misconception%20about%20Taiwan%20is%20that%20we're%20always%20under%20siege%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221143%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Teachey%20at%20the%20overlook%20of%20Qingshui%20Cliff%2C%20near%20Hualien%2C%20Taiwan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552f40258cf5fbccb95f7e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Teachey%20at%20the%20overlook%20of%20Qingshui%20Cliff%2C%20near%20Hualien%2C%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Teachey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20folks%20in%20the%20US%20don't%20know%20enough%20about%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20I've%20spoken%20to%20are%20worried%20about%20coming%20here%20because%20of%20geopolitical%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20here%2C%20I%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20many%20Chinese%20military%20planes%20were%20entering%20Taiwan's%20Air%20Defense%20Identification%20Zone%2C%20or%20ADIZ%2C%20each%20day.%20I%20felt%20like%20maybe%20I%20had%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20frying%20pan%20and%20into%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20when%20exactly%20it%20switched%2C%20but%20at%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20I%20realized%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20just%20background%20noise.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20threat%20is%20certainly%20real%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20go%20about%20our%20lives%2C%20and%20we%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ENovember%2015%2C%2012%3A49%20p.m.%20SGT%3A%20This%20story%20has%20been%20updated%20to%20clarify%20Teachey's%20reaction%20to%20geopolitical%20threats%20in%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-yorker-moved-taiwan-salary-lifestyle-rent-comparison-essay-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700024013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65530e9d385143459e8c64d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-yorker-moved-taiwan-salary-lifestyle-rent-comparison-essay-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alex%20Teachey%2C%2038%2C%20made%20the%20move%20to%20Taiwan%20after%2017%20years%20in%20New%20York.%20Despite%20the%20pay%20cut%2C%20he%20says%20he%20prefers%20living%20in%20Taipei.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-yorker-moved-taiwan-salary-lifestyle-rent-comparison-essay-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Subtle%20Art%20of%20Ignoring%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15100751%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemonetisation%E2%80%99s%20anniversary%20came%20and%20went%2C%20without%20any%20defence%20of%20the%20masterstroke%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Notebandi%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20from%20Latur%2C%20Maharashtra.%20Anil%20Bokil%20runs%20an%20institution%20called%20%E2%80%98ArthaKranti%E2%80%99%20(economic%20revolution)%2C%20and%20calls%20himself%20as%20an%20economic%20theorist.%20His%20thinking%3A%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%20where%2070%25%20of%20people%20survive%20on%20just%20Rs%20150%20per%20day%2C%20why%20do%20we%20need%20currency%20notes%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%20100%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20abolished%2086%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20currency%20how%20the%20PM%20got%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202013%2C%20soon%20after%20Modi%20was%20declared%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20PM%20candidate%2C%20Bokil%20went%20to%20Ahmedabad%20with%20his%20colleagues%20and%20made%20a%20presentation%20about%20an%20ArthaKranti%20proposal.%20Modi%20gave%20Bokil%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20time%20I%20was%20done%2C%20I%20realised%20he%20had%20listened%20to%20me%20for%2090%20minutes.%20He%20said%20nothing%20after%20I%20made%20my%20presentation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20surprising.%20The%20idea%20that%20a%20simple%2C%20magical%20and%20transformational%20action%20could%20be%20executed%20would%20have%20transfixed%20Modi.%20On%20the%20ArthaKranti%20website%2C%20the%20benefits%20of%20demonetisation%20conveyed%20to%20Modi%20are%20listed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTerrorist%20and%20anti-national%20activities%20would%20be%20controlled%2C%20the%20motive%20for%20tax%20avoidance%20would%20be%20reduced%2C%20corruption%20would%20be%20minimised%2C%20(also)%20a%20significant%20growth%20in%20employment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20not%20to%20like%3F%20But%20there%20are%20no%20details%20about%20any%20of%20this%20nor%20how%20demonetisation%20would%20be%20executed%20and%20its%20benefits%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reference%20to%20or%20analysis%20of%20what%20the%20fallout%20could%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthaKranti%20also%20proposed%20withdrawing%20the%20entire%20taxation%20system%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20transaction%20tax%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%202%2C000%20limit%20on%20cash%20transactions.%20Its%20ideas%20were%20reductive%2C%20simplistic%20and%2C%20apparently%2C%20easy%20to%20implement.%20It%20was%20perfect%20for%20Modi%2C%20who%20picked%20out%20the%20single%20most%20dramatic%20element%20from%20this%3A%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20on%20November%208%2C%202016%2C%20Modi%20said%20India%E2%80%99s%20problems%20were%20corruption%2C%20black%20money%20and%20terrorism.%20Strong%20steps%20must%20be%20taken%20against%20these%2C%20and%20he%20would%20take%20them.%20Indians%20were%20honest%20but%20India%20was%20corrupt%2C%20and%20so%20a%20decisive%20step%20was%20needed%20against%20corruption%2C%20black%20money%20and%20terrorism.%20Had%20people%20ever%20thought%20about%20where%20money%20for%20terrorism%20came%20from%2C%20Modi%20asked.%20It%20came%20from%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20counterfeiting%20operations%20in%20India%2C%20which%20was%20proved%20by%20the%20frequent%20arrests.%20He%20said%20the%20circulation%20of%20cash%20was%20linked%20to%20corruption%3A%20this%20was%20why%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20notes%20were%20between%2080%25%20and%2090%25%20of%20the%20total%20currency.%20He%20was%20cancelling%20them%20as%20legal%20tender%20in%20four%20hours%2C%20at%20midnight.%20That%20meant%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20notes%20currently%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20anti-national%20people%20would%20become%20worthless%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-curious-case-of-the-missing-rbi-and-its-voice%5C%22%3EThe%20Curious%20Case%20of%20the%20Missing%20RBI%20and%20Its%20Voice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20acknowledged%20there%20would%20be%20some%20discomfort%20through%20this%20policy%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20problem.%20Ordinary%20citizens%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%20enthusiastic%20about%20sacrifice%20and%20hardship%20for%20the%20country.%20No%20preparation%20was%20made%20by%20various%20departments%20and%20we%20know%20this%20because%20the%20Cabinet%20was%20summoned%20on%20November%208%20and%20ministers%20were%20told%20to%20leave%20their%20mobiles%20behind%20so%20the%20act%20could%20remain%20secret%20till%20it%20was%20announced.%20Since%20ministers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%20their%20departments%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20and%20nobody%20prepared%2C%20just%20as%20in%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20been%20specifically%20warned%20by%20the%20RBI%2C%20the%20body%20that%20actually%20had%20to%20demonetise%20the%20notes%20of%20currency%20its%20governor%20guaranteed%20with%20his%20signature%20and%20was%20arm-twisted%20into%20doing%20so%2C%20that%20demonetisation%20was%20a%20mistake.%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20resigned%20as%20governor%20after%20having%20discussed%20and%20disapproved%20of%20this%20move.%20The%20new%20governor%2C%20Urjit%20Patel%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20accept%20it%20by%20Modi%20within%20weeks%20of%20taking%20office.%20He%20then%20refused%20to%20release%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20the%20RBI%20urgently%20held%20on%205.30%20pm%20on%20November%208%20(just%20before%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech)%20to%20approve%20the%20unhinged%20move%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FuTs1pjrHeVUrpVJ6gPKNMP%2FRBI-cites-threat-to-life-national-security-as-Modis-noteb.html%5C%22%3Eciting%20national%20security%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20to%20life%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20minutes%20were%20finally%20leaked%20to%20the%20press%20two%20years%20later%20in%20November%202018%2C%20Patel%20quit%20and%20left%20the%20following%20month.%20The%20RBI%20minutes%20said%20it%20was%20told%20by%20the%20government%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20economy%20had%20grown%2030%25%20between%202011%20and%202016%20but%20the%20currency%20notes%20of%20higher%20denomination%20had%20grown%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20cash%20was%20the%20facilitator%20for%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20counterfeit%20money%20of%20around%20Rs%20400%20crores%20was%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20notes%20should%20be%20made%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20government%20was%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20the%20economic%20growth%20referred%20to%20by%20the%20government%20was%20real%20while%20the%20rise%20in%20currency%20was%20nominal%20and%20not%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%20and%20%E2%80%9Chence%20this%20argument%20does%20not%20adequately%20support%20the%20recommendation%E2%80%9D%20for%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20most%20black%20money%20was%20in%20land%20or%20gold%20and%20not%20cash%2C%20and%20abolishing%20currency%20would%20have%20no%20effect%20on%20curbing%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20demonetisation%20would%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20Rs%20400%20crores%20in%20counterfeit%20currency%20was%20insignificant%20(only%200.02%25)%20compared%20to%20the%20total%20cash%20in%20circulation%3A%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20all%20this%2C%20the%20RBI%20board%20nonetheless%20put%20its%20rubber%20stamp%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20idea.%20The%20reason%20why%20it%20fought%20to%20keep%20this%20capitulation%20secret%20is%20clear.%20It%20had%20done%20its%20job%20in%20pushing%20back%20and%20pointing%20out%20the%20flaws%3B%20it%20was%20now%20protecting%20Modi.%20That%20is%20why%20Urjit%20Patel%20shamefully%20claimed%20there%20was%20a%20national%20security%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20he%20could%20not%20reveal%20the%20minutes%2C%20when%20RTI%20activists%20sought%20to%20access%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20events%20proved%20that%20on%20every%20count%20the%20RBI%20had%20accurately%20predicted%20both%20the%20damage%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20benefit.%20What%20the%20RBI%20was%20hiding%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20Modi%20had%20ignored%20its%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true%20%E2%80%94%20and%20gone%20ahead%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700023130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15100751%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202016%2C%20the%20RBI%20had%20accurately%20predicted%20both%20the%20damage%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20benefit%20of%20the%20demonetisation.%20Was%20it%20heard%3F%20No.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20says%20China%20has%20'real%20problems'%20ahead%20of%20key%20US%20summit%20with%20Xi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700023082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105224439%2Cimgsize-796422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-says-china-has-real-problems-ahead-of-key-us-summit-with-xi%2Farticleshow%2F105224220.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105224220.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20expressed%20that%20China%20has%20%26quot%3Breal%20problems%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20fundraising%20event%20in%20San%20Francisco%20ahead%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20The%20leaders%20will%20meet%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%2C%20their%20first%20encounter%20in%20a%20year.%20Biden%2