ms.%20It%20has%20also%20not%20revoked%20the%20previous%20BJP%20govt%E2%80%99s%20Hijab%20ban%2C%E2%80%9D%20Owaisi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20CongRSS%20govt%20has%20banned%20HIJAB%20in%20exams.%20It%20has%20also%20not%20revoked%20the%20previous%20BJP%20govt%E2%80%99s%20Hijab%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20CongRSS%20chief%20RSS%20Anna%20wants%20to%20apply%20%E2%80%9CKarnataka%20model%E2%80%9D%20in%20Telangana.%20This%20is%20why%20he%20keeps%20abusing%20sherwani%20%26amp%3B%20avoids%20being%20seen%20with%20skull%20cap%20wearing%20Muslims%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20(%40asadowaisi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasadowaisi%2Fstatus%2F1724398491676340478%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20meanwhile%20asked%20Congress%20leaders%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20work%20on%20revoking%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20hijab%20ban%2C%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fomar-abdullah-asks-congress-to-revoke-hijab-ban-in-karnataka-2769788%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20the%20government%20interfere%20in%20this%3F%20And%20such%20orders%20are%20passed%20through%20which%20Muslims%20are%20targeted.%20When%20all%20this%20used%20to%20happen%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier%2C%20it%20would%20not%20surprise%20us%20because%20there%20was%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700018035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.