ie%20Myers%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrist.org%2Fpolitics%2Fjoe-manchin-senate-jim-justice-climate%2F%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dnewsletter%26utm_campaign%3Ddaily%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrist%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supreme%20irony%20is%20that%20while%20Manchin%20was%20the%20fiercest%20defender%20of%20coal%20among%20Senate%20Democrats%2C%20his%20greatest%20single%20legacy%20will%20be%20major%20climate%20legislation%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Bledsoe%2C%20a%20lecturer%20at%20American%20University's%20Center%20for%20Environmental%20Policy%20and%20a%20former%20Senate%20staffer%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eenews.net%2Farticles%2Fsizing-up-manchins-legacy-on-energy-climate-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EE%26amp%3BE%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20points%20to%20a%20much%20more%20complex%20person%20and%20nuanced%20policy%20figure%20than%20the%20caricatures%20painted%20by%20activists%20on%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManchin%20was%20one%20of%20the%20key%20senators%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-heres-whats-in-the-manchin-deal-for-bidens-agenda-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%20of%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20set%20aside%20%24370%20billion%20in%20spending%20and%20tax%20credits%20to%20jumpstart%20the%20green%20energy%20transition.%20The%20bill%20marked%20the%20largest%20investment%20the%20US%20has%20ever%20made%20to%20combat%20climate%20change.%20It%20passed%20after%20a%20last-minute%20deal%20was%20struck%20by%20Manchin%20and%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerry%20Petrella%2C%20a%20former%20top%20aide%20to%20Schumer%2C%20told%20E%26amp%3BE%20that%20how%20Manchin%20is%20remembered%20may%20ultimately%20depend%20on%20how%20the%20IRA%20delivers%20on%20its%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20if%20in%20seven%20years%20we%20are%20much%20further%20along%20in%20reducing%20carbon%20and%20growing%20clean%20energy%20jobs%20and%20bringing%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20back%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20none%20of%20the%20name-calling%20matters.%20He%20helped%20design%20the%20bill%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20provide%20the%2050th%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20if%20Manchin%20were%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%20Democrat%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20the%20climate%20agenda.%20But%20perhaps%20Manchin's%20greatest%20strength%20as%20a%20Democrat%20was%20his%20ability%20to%20hold%20his%20seat%20in%20an%20otherwise%20staunchly%20red%20West%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20West%20Virginia%20overwhelmingly%20voted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-trial-experts-offer-chillaxed-theory-of-asset-valuation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202016%20and%202020%20elections%2C%20Manchin%20easily%20won%20reelection%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Manchin%20gone%2C%20his%20successor%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20a%20Republican%20%E2%80%94%20most%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-justice-babydog-state-address-lifting-dog-bette-midler-video-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWest%20Virginia%20Gov.%20Jim%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20announced%20in%20April%20he%20was%20running%20to%20unseat%20Manchin.%20Justice%2C%20like%20Manchin%2C%20made%20his%20fortune%20in%20part%20through%20family-owned%20coal%20mines.%20Thanks%20to%20his%20GOP%20credentials%20and%20embrace%20of%20Trump%2C%20he's%20even%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20climate%20ally%20than%20Manchin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20whose%20Senate%20majority%20is%20already%20slim%2C%20could%20lose%20that%20Senate%20seat%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%20%E2%80%94%20making%20any%20climate%20bill