quot%3B%20that%20helps%20get%20the%20outcome%20you%20want%2C%20and%20then%20show%20your%20math%2C%20said%20Trump's%20second%20expert%2C%20Washington%20DC-based%20forensic%20accountant%20Jason%20Flemmons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20choices%20are%20many%2C%20Flemmons%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20property's%20worth%20could%20be%20its%20%26quot%3Bliquidation%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20its%20%26quot%3Breproduction%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20You%20can%20use%20its%20%26quot%3Bassessed%20value%20for%20property%20tax%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20also%20value%20a%20property%20based%20on%20what%20comparable%20properties%20recently%20sold%20for%2C%20or%20on%20what%20any%20range%20of%20appraisers%20say%20it's%20worth%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20judgement%20call%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20any%20of%20the%20different%20methods%20be%20more%20right%2C%20or%20more%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%20Trump%20defense%20lawyer%20Jesus%20Suarez%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20answered%2C%20providing%20that%20it's%20a%20recognized%20method.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20wrong%20or%20right%20method%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20long%20as%20you%20choose%20one%20of%20them%20and%20you%20disclose%20what%20you're%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20two%20defense%20expert%20witnesses%20were%20markedly%20different%20from%20each%20other%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20objectivity%20and%20experience.%20The%20first%2C%20Witkoff%2C%20is%20a%20self-described%20Trump%20friend%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherealdeal.com%2Fnew-york%2F2020%2F09%2F21%2Fthat-was-a-business-decision-why-real-estate-execs-are-backing-trump-or-backing-away%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongtime%20fundraiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fellow%20developer%20who%20had%20never%20been%20an%20expert%20witness%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seco