0the%20major%20studios%2C%20US%20television%20networks%20and%20streaming%20services%20like%20Netflix%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Apple%20TV%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20members%20still%20need%20to%20formally%20approve%20the%20deal%20but%20most%20expect%20the%20vote%20will%20be%20strongly%20in%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actors%E2%80%99%20strike%2C%20and%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-writers-reach-tentative-deal-with-studios%2Fa-66912366%5C%22%3EHollywood%E2%80%99s%20Writers%20Guild%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20WGA%2C%20which%20lasted%20from%20May%20through%20September%20this%20year%2C%20effectively%20shut%20down%20film%20and%20TV%20production%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20movies%20and%20series%20were%20able%20to%20secure%20interim%20agreements%20from%20the%20union%20to%20keep%20shooting%2C%20many%20hit%20shows%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EEmily%20in%20Paris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Last%20of%20Us%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ELaw%20and%20Order%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20White%20Lotus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EYellowstone%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20blockbuster%20films%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EGladiator%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EAvatar%3C%2Fem%3E%20sequels%2C%20as%20well%20as%20new%20%3Cem%3ETransformers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESpider-Man%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESuperman%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0movies%2C%20were%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%2C%20both%20actors%20and%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cbelow-the-line%E2%80%9D%20employees%2C%20from%20set%20designers%20to%20audio%20technicians%20to%20make-up%20stylists%2C%20lost%20their%20jobs.%20The%20economic%20damage%20to%20the%20US%C2%A0economy%20runs%20into%20the%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20also%20disrupted%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20promotional%20ecosystem%2C%20since%20actors%20were%20prohibited%20from%20promoting%20their%20movies%20at%20premieres%20and%20red%20carpet%20events%20while%20negotiations%20were%20still%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20films%2C%20notably%20%3Cem%3EDune%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChallengers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20both%20starring%20Zendaya%2C%20delayed%20their%20releases%20until%20next%20year%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20stars%20will%20be%20available%20to%20promote%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOscar%20promotion%20can%20kick-off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20strike%20is%20also%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20Oscar%20season%2C%20which%20can%20now%20kick%20off%20in%20earnest%20with%20award%C2%A0contenders%20available%20to%20do%20the%20rounds%20of%20talk%20shows%20and%20magazine%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestarting%20Hollywood%20could%20bring%20its%20own%20problems%2C%20however.%20As%20everyone%20rushes%20to%20get%20their%20movies%20and%20shows%20into%20production%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20risk%20of%20a%20bottleneck%20as%20demand%20for%20actors%2C%20cinematographers%2C%20editors%2C%20and%20costume%20designers%20outstrips%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20getting%20the%20dream%20machine%20going%20again.%20The%20studios%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20were%20desperate%20to%20reach%20a%20deal%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20salvaging%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20broadcast%20TV%20schedule%20and%20getting%20enough%20films%20shot%20and%20in%20the%20can%20before%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%C2%A0issues%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20contract%20negotiation%2C%20the%20actors%20strike%20was%20about%20wages%2C%20and%20with%20the%20new%20deal%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20secured%20a%20substantial%20bump%20in%20minimum%20rates%20%E2%80%93%20the%20base%20daily%20salary%20for%20a%20union%20actor%20on%20a%20film%20or%20TV%20shoot%20%E2%80%93%20for%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20battle%20was%20over%20the%20future.%20The%20new%20technologies%20of%20streaming%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20dominated%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHollywood%E2%80%99s%20creative%20classes%20felt%20global%20streamers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20properly%20compensating%20them%20for%20their%20work.%20An%20actor%20or%20writer%20on%20a%20television%20series%20typically%20gets%20paid%20an%20upfront%20salary%20plus%20compensation%2C%20or%20residuals%2C%20every%20time%20the%20show%20is%20rerun%2C%20or%20sold%20to%20a%20cable%20channel%20or%20international%20broadcaster.%20Netflix%20and%20co.%20broke%20that%20model%20by%20doing%20buy-out%20deals%2C%20paying%20talent%20a%20one-time%20lump%20sum%20to%20acquire%20a%20series%20worldwide%20to%20show%20on%20their%20platform%20in%20perpetuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20SAG-AFTRA%20deal%2C%20talent%20working%20on%20big-budget%20streaming%20series%20and%20movies%20will%20get%20a%20100%20percent%20bump%20in%20performance%20compensation%20bonuses%20if%20their%20work%20is%20a%20hit%2C%20meaning%20it%20crosses%20certain%20viewership%20thresholds.%20While%20this%20is%20unlikely%20to%20mean%20much%20for%20most%20union%20members%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bulk%20of%20Netflix%20series%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20hits%20%E2%80%94%20it%20marks%20a%20sea%20change%20by%20requiring%20streamers%20to%20share%20their%20profits%20with%20the%20people%20who%C2%A0make%20their%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3EArtificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20an%20even%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fai-and-film-actors-and-writers-fear-obsolescence%2Fa-66307353%5C%22%3Ebigger%20sticking%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20unions%20determined%20to%20limit%20how%20the%20studios%20and%20streamers%20could%20use%20new%20AI%C2%A0technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20in%20particular%20were%20worried%20studios%20and%20streamers%20would%20begin%20to%20use%20AI%C2%A0scans%20of%20their%20likenesses%20and%20voice%20performances%20to%20insert%20them%20into%20new%20films%20and%20shows%20without%20their%20approval%20or%20compensation.%20This%20is%20a%20real%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBlack%20Widow%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0star%C2%A0Scarlett%20Johansson%20recently%20took%20legal%20action%20against%20an%20AI%C2%A0app%20that%C2%A0used%20her%20name%20and%20likeness%20in%20an%20online%20advertisement%20without%20her%20permission.%20Last%20month%2C%20Tom%20Hanks%20took%C2%A0to%20Instagram%20to%20warn%20his%20fans%20that%20a%20dental%20plan%20was%20using%20an%20unapproved%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20him%20for%20one%20of%20their%20promotional%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20SAG-AFTRA%20deal%20puts%20guardrails%20on%20the%20use%20of%20AI%C2%A0and%20requires%20producers%20to%20secure%20approval%20to%20scan%20and%20reuse%20an%20actors%E2%80%99%20performance.%20The%20AMPTP%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20keep%20meeting%20with%20the%20union%20over%20the%20next%20two%20and%20half%20years%20until%20the%20next%20contract%20negotiations%2C%20to%20discuss%20AI%C2%A0as%20the%20technology%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20shift%20in%20Hollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20fiercest%20labor%20dispute%20in%20a%20generation%20comes%20to%20a%20close%2C%20the%20creatives%2C%20not%20the%20suits%2C%20appear%20the%20clear%20winners.%20Most%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20demands%20were%20met%20and%20the%20union%20secured%20concessions%20on%20the%20most%20contentious%20issues%2C%20including%20streaming%20compensation%20and%20restrictions%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solidarity%20within%20the%20union%20%E2%80%93%20big%20stars%20like%20George%20Clooney%2C%20Scarlett%20Johansson%2C%20and%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20strike%2C%20alongside%20rank-and-file%20members%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20source%20of%20strength%20for%20SAG-AFTRA%20negotiators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20o