%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20Vyam%20expanded%20her%20art%20canvas.%20She%20began%20making%20drawings%20for%20booklets%20published%20by%20the%20Eklavya%20Foundation.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20they%20became%20popular%2C%20I%20was%20approached%20by%20Chennai-based%20Tara%20Books%20for%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Vyam%20and%20her%20husband%20proudly%20declare%20their%20most%20iconic%20project%20to%20be%20illustrating%20for%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98Bhimayana%3A%20Experiences%20of%20Untouchability%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20chronicles%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20couple%20have%20illustrated%20children%E2%80%99s%20novels%2C%20history%20fiction%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325545%2Fmust-watch-films-and-shows-on-disability-pride-and-representation-in-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiographies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20more.%20In%202008%2C%20Vyam%20was%20awarded%20the%20BolognaRagazzi%20award%20for%20her%20illustrations%20in%20%E2%80%98The%20Night%20Life%20of%20Trees%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20I%20ask%20Vyam%20about%20these%20accolades%2C%20expecting%20an%20elaborate%20answer%2C%20she%20shrugs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy.%20The%20awards%20make%20me%20happy.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20feeling%20to%20see%20my%20%3Cem%3Edignas%3C%2Fem%3E%20getting%20so%20much%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699972262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhopal-based%20Gond%20artist%20Durgabai%20Vyam's%20nature-inspired%20art%20and%20culturally-rooted%20motifs%20have%20gained%20national%20and%20international%20acclaim%2C%20earning%20her%20the%20prestigious%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202022.%22%2C%22a