%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0At%20the%20young%20age%20of%2021%2C%20Ashish%20started%20a%20business%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20young%20and%20naive%20and%20could%20not%20really%20sustain%20it.%20I%20decided%20to%20close%20it%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20While%20the%20business%20had%20to%20be%20closed%2C%20it%20ignited%20a%20spirit%20in%20Ashish%20to%20run%20a%20successful%20business%20one%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1-1699540109-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%C2%A0%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Ashish%20Dokania%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pursued%20an%20MBA%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20started%20his%20career%20in%20the%20banking%20sector.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20with%20the%20bank%2C%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20project%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254648%2Fbengaluru-credr-electric-ev-startup-second-hand-petrol-scooter-new-ebike-two-wheeler-ather-exchange-honda-activa-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancing%20transactions%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20a%20lot%20of%20infrastructure%20projects%20which%20kind%20of%20exposed%20me%20to%20renewable%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202015%2C%20he%20joined%20another%20firm%20which%20worked%20along%20similar%20lines%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20solar%20energy.%20Working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20for%20several%20years%20is%20what%20became%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20he%20perceived%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20long%20list%20of%20existing%20innovations%20like%20%E2%80%98battery%20swap%E2%80%99%20and%20longer%20range%20in%20two-wheeler%20EVs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20realised%20working%20in%20the%20sector%20was%20that%20with%20renewable%20energies%20that%20are%20dependent%20on%20nature%2C%20you%20cannot%20predict%20it%20as%20per%20your%20demand.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20EVs%2C%20there%20will%20soon%20be%20a%20huge%20gap%20in%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20renewable%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20line%20of%20thought%20prompted%20me%20to%20consider%20a%20solution%20similar%20to%20the%20setup%20we%20employ%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20with%20electricity%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20and%20a%20generator%20or%20inverter%20as%20a%20backup.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20equipped%20with%20a%20petrol%20engine%20as%20a%20standby%20power%20source%20to%20ensure%20complete%20reliability%20for%20the%20consumer%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20came%20to%20Ashish.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20built%20the%20hybrid%20as%20a%20retrofit%20solution%20to%20give%20a%20bridge%20to%2025%20crore%20existing%20two-wheeler%20riders%20in%20the%20country%20towards%20a%20greener%20tomorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20early%202020%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%2015%20years%20of%20corporate%20career%20and%20finally%20bring%20his%20childhood%20dream%20to%20a%20living%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332299%2Fbengaluru-chef-elizabeth-yorke-upcycles-brewery-byproducts-into-sustainable-food-items%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresent%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20has%20converted%20over%2050%20vehicles%20into%20their%20hybrid%20models.%20Of%20those%2025%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20company%20by%20the%20consumers%20themselves.%20It%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20converted%20vehicles%20have%20undergone%20rigorous%20testing%2C%20covering%20a%20total%20distance%20of%20one%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20lakh%20kilometres%20over%20the%20past%2018%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHigher%20range%2C%20cheaper%20transition%20and%20additional%20features%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20vehicles%20can%20switch%20from%20petrol%20to%20electric%20battery.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333969%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20vehicles%20can%20switch%20from%20petrol%20to%20electric%20battery.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Ashish%20Dokania%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20lies%20in%20sustainability%20and%20eco-friendly%20business%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20have%20companies%20producing%20EVs%20and%20petrol%20vehicles.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20already%20crores%20of%20vehicles%20on%20the%20road%20that%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20more%20greener%20vehicles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%20of%20converting%20a%20regular%20petrol%20scooter%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98dual%20powertrain%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20conversion%20process%20basically%20entails%20placing%20the%20entire%20motor%2C%20the%20entire%20electric%20powertrain%2C%20which%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20petrol%20vehicle%2C%20without%20displacing%20the%20original%20petrol%20engine.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20examine%20a%20typical%20scooter%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20that%20its%20engine%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20left-hand%20side%20at%20the%20rear%2C%20making%20the%20scooter%20inherently%20unbalanced%20and%20tilted%20towards%20the%20left.%20What%20our%20innovation%20involves%20is%20relocating%20the%20entire%20electric%20powertrain%20to%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20This%20adjustment%20effectively%20rebalances%20the%20scooter%2C%20offering%20a%20more%20stable%20and%20balanced%20ride%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20controller%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283991%2Fnoise-top-smartwatch-brand-india-gaurav-amit-khatri-bikaner-success-startup-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20display%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20indicates%20the%20amount%20of%20battery%20left%20and%20which%20mode%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20indicates%20if%20there%20is%20any%20fault%20in%20the%20system%20or%20if%20there%20is%20a%20heating%20problem%20while%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on%20electric%20mode%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dual%20powertrain%20mode%20or%20the%20retrofits%20are%20great%20not%20just%20because%20they%20are%20eco-friendly%20but%20it%20also%20reduces%20the%20anxiety%20of%20the%20rider%20over%20its%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20a%20typical%20rider%20only%20uses%20their%20scooter%20for%20a%20range%20of%2050%20to%2060%20km.%20It%20is%20only%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20once%20a%20month%20that%20they%20might%20need%20to%20use%20it%20for%20another%20100%20or%20200%20km.%20So%20instead%20of%20giving%20the%20consumer%20more%20range%20or%20battery%20swap%2C%20what%20we%20gave%20them%20is%20a%20reliable%20petrol%20engine%20that%20will%20cover%20any%20extra%20distance%20that%20you%20want%20to%20travel%20on%20a%20given%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20saves%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20would%20otherwise%20be%20spent%20on%20petrol%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22